Description: 你去过一所崇尚故事的房屋.
Name: _REUSE

Description: 未来的某一天,这将会是你的国家的旗帜. [装配到附属物槽位.]
Name: 即将到来的荣耀旗帜

ChangeDescriptionText: 0|You have finished opening a cache of curiosities.
Description: 满满一箱神秘的物品. 打开它!
Name: 一箱未知的东西

Description: 一名不善言辞的将军把那里命名为玛瑙港. 之后她发现那里到处都是蓝宝石. 想想她对此有多尴尬.
Name: 一箱蓝宝石

Description: 这名神秘而恍惚的学者正向珊瑚之源旅行.
Name: 奇怪的人

Description: 这里还有许多等待发现的东西. 但是这已经满足需要了.
Name: 一份综合港口报告: 手掌帝国

AvailableAt: 爱古
Description: 一份对于当地事物不甚全面的描述.
Name: 一份综合港口报告: 爱古

Description: 一份和令人愉快的女探险家会面的邀请. (这将继续手掌帝国的故事)
Name: A Delightful Invitation

Description: 把这带给手掌帝国换取奖励
Name: 氢气运输

Description: 你有一名专业的, 甚至可能是有从业执照的医生的帮助.
Name: A Doctor Aboard

Description: 这是猩红之书的一个章节,那是一本声名狼藉的爱情故事合集.大巴扎的领主寻找了它很长时间.
Name: 红色之梦

Description: 如果你是个没有原则的人,这能给你带来很多利润. [这东西就算是合法使用也太过危险. 把它带到伦敦时要格外小心.]
Name: 一小桶红蜂蜜

Description: 悬浮在一片看起来像是海盐碎块的东西中. 手掌帝国那位高贵的总管主张这会很有用.
Name: 凝冻的一滴红蜂蜜
A Gift for the Monkey Emperor

Description: 刚从地面来的,只是有一点点擦伤.
Name: 给海盗王的礼物

Description: 它被精心地上了一遍漆, 它的眼睛闪着光, 看起来让人很有食欲.
Name: 给怅然若失的女恶魔的礼物

Description: 猫岛海盗王对你信任的象征.
Name: 笼子花园的钥匙

Description: 他在被绘画时不会不戴帽子.
Name: 里面是衣冠楚楚男士肖像的吊坠

Description: 她从没真正笑过.
Name: 里面是可爱的女士肖像的挂坠

Description: 一个水手的宝藏对另一个水手来说就是垃圾.但是这看起来很有意思...
Name: 埋藏了很长时间的宝藏

Description: 它闪着月蓝色的光. 为了争夺这样一块蓝色闪晶,人们不惜发动战争. [你能找到这东西的用处: 也许令人惊恐的学者会购买这东西.]
Name: 帕默斯顿山

Description: 事实上,不是奇迹. 但是他们永远不能接近到能看出其中的差别的距离.
Name: A Manual of Miracles

Description: 没有封印, 但是用了一种地狱内部通信用文字书写.
Name: 怅然若失的女恶魔寄出的信

Description: 里面溢出了一些愤怒的光.有些时候它会发出咯咯声.最好不要打开它.
Name: 一个捕光镜匣,装满了愤怒的梦蚺

Description: 梦中的绿色 大蛇的琉璃绿色皮肤 还有写满了文字的纸片
Name: 镜子护身符

AvailableAt: 覆叶的继承人可以做这个手术.
Description: 覆叶的继承人从你身上摘下了什么.
Name: 失踪的耳垂

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Welcome aboard, stranger.~0|A certain matter has become clear.
Description: 你让一名陌生人上了船.这可能意味着一些事情会发生.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Consequences wait.
Name: A New Face

Description: "醒目的月蓝, 记忆和最明亮的珊瑚的蓝色."
Name: '地虹'书卷的一页: 月蓝

Description: "星海黄色的C字母,记忆中太阳的颜色. 那些丰饶的,发出臭气的,真菌类的生物: 这些全都在星海黄的光辉中茁壮成长."
Name: '地虹'书卷的一页: 星海黄

Description: "G代表着消逝的刚特褐灰, 是所有其他颜色被吞噬后所剩下的遗骸. 刚特褐灰可以在无尽的阴影中找到."
Name: '地虹'书卷的一页: 刚特褐灰

Description: "I代表靛紫.没人记得为什么.靛紫为家中被遗忘的角落染色."
Name: '地虹'书卷的一页: 靛紫

Description: "P字母用黯蓝书写, 最深的海中的颜色. [有人在页边潦草的写道: 在大門之後是一片更無光的海]"
Name: '地虹'书卷的一页: 黯蓝

Description: "V 代表着黯紫罗兰,这血液的颜色要从尖端流出. 黯紫罗兰色的墨水用来签署最令人绝望的条约..."
Name: '地虹'书卷的一页: 黯紫羅蘭

Description: "在你的镜子之中, V 代表琉璃绿, 半梦半醒的颜色."
Name: '地虹'书卷的一页: 琉璃绿

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Before now, you didn't have the Parabox.~0|Before now, you had the Parabox.
Description: 伊瑞暮的有些东西令人难以理解. 它真的能保护你免受太阳光的伤害吗?
Name: 悖论宝盒

Description: 高雅的总管给了你这个，用它来杀死困扰手掌帝国的食人海盗.
Name: 特制剧毒

Description: 通向地表的路, 工程学的奇迹. 将军对这里有适中的兴趣.
Name: 敷衍的港口报告: 卡米安运河

Description:
研究空地中间那棵不可能生长在地下的树, 关于一名船长撕毁画着大蛇的画像. 船长的船员在旁边冷静地观看着. 其中一个人口中分叉的舌头清晰可见. 绘画上被涂满了琉璃绿 - 半梦半醒的颜色, 这种颜色在地面无法看到.
你就是画中的船长; 你也是作画的那个人.
Name: 一次与幽灵的邂逅, 189-, 船长 ------

Description: The nuns endure.
Name: 港口报告: 修道院岩礁

Description: 通向古大陆的大门! 吞噬幼稚者之地.
Name: 港口报告: 亚当之路

Description: 光芒耀眼而炽热. 很少有人能忍受那里的强光.
Name: 港口报告: 阿斯蒂沃

AvailableAt: 爱古
Description: 一份关于爱古处Fortas Kettle中正在进行的事情的报告.
Name: 港口报告: 爱古

AvailableAt: 在安忒获取
Description: 一份关于那盛开的港口中诸多事务的报告.
Name: 港口报告: 安忒

Description: You have seen where the world ends. Behind those peaks of ice, something colder by far.
Name: 港口报告: 渴求之地平线

Description: 那些流亡者不说话,那些猴子则只是暴躁的发出吱吱声. 尽管如此,这里也有信息值得收集.
Name: 港口报告: 法典岛

AvailableAt: 这一定是在达哈写的.
Description: 一份关于达哈城中实际情况的报告.
Name: 港口报告: 达哈

Description: 伦敦对这里最近的事情几乎不感兴趣.
Name: 港口报告: 德莫岛

Description: 这个岛上最近的新闻是那些偷灵魂的猿类. 科学的讲, 是猴子.
Name: 港口报告: 手掌帝国

Description: 是嘶嘶. 是嘶嘶. 我们太嘶嘶了解了. 我们到家了.
Name: 港口报告: 陷落的伦敦

Description: 原始的海冰之塔. 一个关于问题和谜语的营地.
Name: 港口报告: 寒霜城

Description: 诸多相关信息中, 海军尤其对海盗做的生意感兴趣.
Name: 港口报告: 加德的哀悼

Description: 一块坠落的钟乳石: 一个塞满了战利品的僧院.
Name: 港口报告: 神落

Description: 有效率的工人们精神饱满的唱着歌. 敏锐的眼睛在观察着.
Name: 港口报告: 宏伟晶洞

Description: 建立在巨兽背上一座一直在进行修补的城市. 和平的代价如此之深.
Name: 港口报告: 隐逸之地

Description: An odd place. Best to keep an eye on it.
Name: 港口报告: 猎户塔楼

Description: 你将会来过这里.
Name: 港口报告: 伊瑞暮

Description: 一个建有酒馆和蜜馆的放荡走私者巢穴.
Name: 港口报告: 猫岛

Description: 塔楼上的光消失了.
Name: 港口报告: 猎户塔楼的结局

Description: 明亮, 黑暗, 暴躁, 温柔, 富裕, 绝望. 一个复杂的地方: 就像伦敦一样.
Name: 港口报告: 可汗之心

Description: 长长的绑在一起的船只为流亡者提供了避难所.
Name: 港口报告: 可汗之影

Description: 这里是世界的尽头.
Name: 港口报告: 噬王者的城堡

AvailableAt: 这一定是在沉没的巴内特获得的.
Description: 在谎言与夸大之词中一定隐藏着些许真相.
Name: 港口报告: 沉没的巴内特

Description: A detailed report on a place of interest. The Admiralty would value it.
Name: 港口报告: 帕默斯顿山

Description: 海底的一张巨口, 不法之徒与水中生物的巢穴.
Name: 港口报告: 旮旯

Description: 你很难错过那个雕像.
Name: 港口报告: 农西奥

Description: 两座房子, 都显得很庄严. 那不值得说太多.
Name: 港口报告: 皮格莫特岛

Description: 城在哭喊.
Name: 港口报告: 碎心国

Description: 小伦敦的消费怎么样?
Name: 港口报告: 玛瑙港

Description: 珊瑚源的奇怪事务困扰着伦敦并激起了伦敦的兴趣.
Name: 港口报告: 塞西尔港

Description: 你从来都没在羊岛找到过什么新闻,然而对于将军来说这也是情报.
Name: 港口报告: 贵格避风港

Description: 工厂, 也是商店, 同样也是水下烟草的故乡.
Name: 港口报告: 玫瑰之门

Description: 很值得怀疑.这么少的人是怎么弄丢那么多的悲伤蜘蛛的?
Name: 港口报告: 救世主岩礁

Description: 这曾经是个好地方. 好吧,并没有那么好.
Name: 港口报告: 救世主岩礁 (被毁)

Description: 一座记忆之城, 在此, 历史即战场.
Name: 港口报告: 骨雕馆

Description: 有些事情发生了,或者只是有些人宣称发生了.
Name: 港口报告: 牧羊人岛

Description: On the very edge of London's influence, curious matters are conducted.
Name: 港口报告: 要塞 III

Description: 上百万支点燃的蜡烛. 圣会的聚集地.
Name: 港口报告: 光之礼拜堂

Description: 巨大乌龟壳的遗留. 贪婪的猎人. 腐败中的血肉.
Name: 港口报告: 切洛内特

Description: 城堡只有一小部分可以看见. 但是你能从来来往往的人那里了解到许多关于谁来过这里的信息.
Name: 港口报告: 深寻王的城堡

Description: 远古巨兽走向死亡的被遗忘之深渊.
Name: 港口报告: 刚特极点

Description: "概念就像砖头一样.他可以用来建造理性的法院.或者用它来砸窗户."
Name: 港口报告: 钢铁共和国

Description: 这些湿地里的哲学家们的日常生活是辩论,争吵与祈祷.
Name: 港口报告: 红树学院

Description: 一镐一镐, 学者把这些石头转化为秘密.
Name: 港口报告: 盐狮

Description: 现在来看, 只是一个大蘑菇.
Name: 港口报告: 世纪之蕈

Description: 远方深处的一座孤独灯塔...
Name: 港口报告: 爪下

Description: 这座明亮的瓦尔查斯城严格地限制访客的人数.
Name: 港口报告: 瓦尔查斯

Description: 曾经明亮过,但是瓦尔查斯现在沉默在黑暗中.这种寂静显然带有恶意.
Name: 港口报告: 破碎的瓦尔查斯

Description: 瓦尔查斯依然明亮. 门被锁住了. 外来的访客不再能进入其中.
Name: 港口报告: 闭锁的瓦尔查斯

Description: 死亡侨民用阴谋填满他们的空余时间. 其中一部分阴谋会吸引伦敦的兴趣.
Name: 港口报告: 文登湾

Description: 他们今天是什么? 你之前是什么?
Name: 港口报告: 维瑟吉

Description: 何方为何会有那么多问题?
Name: 港口报告: 何方

Description: 一座监狱岛. 或者瘤节先知的食品柜.
Name: 港口报告: 智慧监狱

Description: 遇难者写诗的地方. 了解爱的地方.
Name: 港口报告: 船墟

Description: 黯紫罗兰: 必要的颜色,但是总是和麻烦连接在一起. 根据其他传统,血液的颜色从尖利的地方流出. 你用黯紫罗兰墨水写下的东西非常难遗忘...
Name: 一瓶黯紫罗兰墨水

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You have what you came for.~0|You have discharged your duty to the Cheery Man.
Description: 你穿过了一片白色的树林, 并带着某种想法归来.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|A cane of pale wood~2|A silvery restorative
Name: A Remedy for the Cheery Man

ChangeDescriptionText: 5|Welcome!~1|Someone is looking for passage.
Description: 伦敦的某人需要你的帮忙.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Someone is looking for passage~5|You welcomed a passenger aboard
Name: 请求搭船

ChangeDescriptionText: 0|You've found the Vengeance of Jonah~1|You've been told of an exceptionally fine restaurant in Venderbight.
Description: "文登湾有这样一个小地方..."
Name: 推荐的餐厅

AvailableAt: 里面的画像是一个小小的金发婴儿.
Description: 从手掌帝国海滨的尸体上找到.
Name: 生锈的吊坠

Description: 这个粘土人用他的灰色巨手抓着捕光镜匣,他看起来有点困惑. 如果他知道应该期待什么,他会看起来比现在困惑得多. [这将能让不知疲倦的机械师睡上一觉.]
Name: 捕蛇陷阱

Description: 这个沉默寡言的女人有些事情要去海盗之林.
Name: 阴沉沉的女士

AvailableAt: 有人会记下船墟的歌.
Description: 来自船墟的旋律
Name: 破壳之歌

Description: 未透露的过往
Name: 一个陌生人

Description: 这是星星的故事.一名崇高天野的流放者戴着面具拿着沉重的包裹, 在下面记录了他的朝圣之行. 并没有圆满的结局.
Name: 旅行中的光

LevelDescriptionText: 1|London~2|Khanate~3|Corsair~4|Zubmarine
Name: 一艘沉船

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Your future captains may convert their ships to zubmarines without cost.
Description: 要将船只变形为潜艇, 请去玛瑙港的蓝宝石加工厂.
Name: 潜航中的秘密

Description: 更深的深处有些东西.
LevelDescriptionText: 4|Abyss of Graves~2|Abyss of Pyres~3|Abyss of Pomegranates~1|Abyss of Scriptures
Name: 深渊仪式: 深渊之上

ChangeDescriptionText: 5|You are face to face with Her Ladyship.~4|She is here.~10|Lady Black will remember you.~1|You have made yourself known.~2|You have purified yourself.~3|You have satisfied yourself.
Description: 她在黑暗中等待着.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|You performed the Ritual of Greeting~2|You performed the Ritual of Hearths~3|You performed the Ritual of Feasting~5|You are face to face with Her Ladyship~4|She is here~10|Lady Black will remember you
Name: 深渊仪式: 接近女士

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Good luck.~0|You rise from the abyss.
Description: 你希望在这深渊中找到什么?
Name: 深渊仪式: 下潜...

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You have partaken in the Rite of Greeting.~2|You have partaken in the Rite of Hearths.~3|You have partaken in the Rite of Feasting.~34|You have partaken in the Rite of Solace.
Description: 你已经不是之前的自己了.
LevelDescriptionText: 0|You have forsaken a rite~1|The Rite of Greeting [This has increased your Hearts by 20 and reduced your Iron by 10.]~2|The Rite of Hearths [This has increased your Mirrors by 20 and reduced your Veils by 10.]~3|The Rite of Feasting [This has increased your Iron by 20 and reduced your Mirrors by 10.]~4|The Rite of Solace [This has increased your Veils by 20 and reduced your Hearts by 10.]
Name: 深渊仪式: 仪式

Description: 姐妹中最小的那个怎么样了?
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Lost in a Fire~2|New Sisters~3|Dark Duties~10|Above the Gulf of Corinth
Name: 相识者: 菲比的命运

ChangeDescriptionText: 2|You are acquainted with the sisters of Hunter's Keep.~10|You are acquainted with the sisters, but something has changed.~1|You know something of Hunter's Keep~25|You've explored the silent house on Hunter's Keep~31|The house on Hunter's Keep is aflame!~40|The house on Hunter's Keep is a blackened shell
Description: 你在猎户塔楼的三姐妹那里逗留过.
LevelDescriptionText: 2|You are acquainted with the sisters~1|You know something of Hunter's Keep~20|You are acquainted with the sisters, but something has changed.
Name: 相识者: 旅居于三姐妹处

ChangeDescriptionText: 10|The Fierce Philanthropist will help you convert your ship to a zubmarine at her hidden workshop.~20|Retrieve zonar schematics from Station III or Khan's Shadow.~30|Return the zonar schematics to the hidden workshop in Port Carnelian.~0|The zubmarine conversion process is complete!
Description: 深渊无法在你面前藏起秘密.
LevelDescriptionText: 10|The Fierce Philanthropist will help you convert your ship to a zubmarine at her hidden workshop~20|Retrieve zonar schematics from Station III or Khan's Shadow~30|Return the zonar schematics to the hidden workshop in Port Carnelian
Name: 获取潜艇

Description: 你是一名贮蜜者葬礼盛宴的荣誉宾客.
Name: 亚当之路: 红桌的宾客

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|The Tree of a Single Day is a hopeful sapling, green and budding.~2|The Tree of a Single Day is tall and strong. Its branches stretch over the rooftops.~3|The Tree of a Single Day is flowering. White petals drift across the square.~5|The Tree of a Single Day cracks and leans. It is time to return to your ship.~4|The Tree of a Single Day is withered. Its gnarled trunk groans.
Description: 它在早晨被种下, 中午就长得很高了,下午出现花蕾,在晚间枯萎. 外国人必须在它倒下之前回到船上.
Name: 亚当之路: 一天中的一棵树

Description: 他们怎么称呼你?
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Madam~2|Sir~3|Citizen~4|my lord~5|my lady~6|Captain~100|(mumble)
Name: 被称作

Description: [这提供少许故事的建议. 卖掉它来移除给船长的建议故事线.]
Name: 给船长的建议

AvailableAt: 在爱古结识.
Description: 你对Fortas Kettle的大副了解多少?
LevelDescriptionText: 20|Seen them through at least one mission~30|Learned some of their deeper secrets~40|Old acquaintances~50|Asked an important question~60|Persuaded the First Mate to abandon Aigul~5|Gained hospitality through a gift of Solacefruits~10|Observed the formation of spines
Name: 爱古: 结识大副

AvailableAt: 在帕默斯顿山或骨雕馆处获取, 在爱古继续.
Description: 威严的姐姐要求你调查他弟弟的悔恨.
LevelDescriptionText: 10|Received a commission~20|Begun drilling for a regret~30|Halfway through drilling for a regret~60|Delivered a regret by way of the Mirror Marches~70|Delivered a regret by way of Prisoner's Honey~80|Delivered a regret in spine form~40|Abandoned drilling for a regret — you may tell the Sister so at Hunter's Keep~45|Advised the sister about abandonment at Hunter's Keep~5|Stopped to listen to the Imperious Sister~55|Grew a regret into spine form~90|Learned the outcome of sending a dream~50|Retrieved a regret. What form will you deliver it in?
Name: 爱古: 受命获取悔恨

AvailableAt: 爱古
Description: 大副在Fortas中种下了棘刺, 问题是到底有多少?
Name: 爱古: 大副的敏感

AvailableAt: 爱古
Description: 这个问题一定要问Fortas Kettle的大副.
Name: 爱古: 关于大副问题的知识

AvailableAt: 爱古
Description: 大副探索爱古苦恨时的悔恨具现.
Name: 爱古: 棘刺要塞

Description: This content is structured but not yet written - AK to complete.
Name: AKContent

Description: AK to add quality reqs and other mechanics.
Name: AKMechanics

Description: 双木匠, 纺织工, 工程师的手,还有老鼠的所有技能.
Name: 白色的修补匠

Description: 一个会思考的生物制作了它, 或者是大海冲刷出来的; 或者二者皆有.
Name: 含混的石器

ChangeDescriptionText: 2|When you finish your tale, Batuk asks a question. He contemplates your answer.~1|Batuk attends closely as you speak.~0|After your tale, Batuk springs to his feet and paces the cavity.~4|Batuk claims he will not rejoin the Seven.~3|Batuk feigns indifference, but you you can tell he's listening.
Description: 他宣称对对抗尼达的七人众没有一点兴趣. [将这个属性降低到0来改变他的态度.]
Name: 志向:  巴图克的冷漠

ChangeDescriptionText: 10|Begin your quest in London.~20|Pursue your ambition on the Isle of Cats.~30|Pursue your ambition at Port Carnelian, with the Fierce Philanthropist.~35|You must search the cities beneath the zee...~40|Find the Philanthropist's husband at Low Barnet, near London.~50|You have given the Philanthropist's locket to Lytton.~60|Pursue your ambition at Scrimshander - seek Mariam in the Ivory Archives.~70|You must restore the Seven Against Nidah.~200|Prepare your plans to conquer Nidah.~300|Seven years pass...~1000|Seven Conquered Nidah.~2000|One Conquered Nidah.~3000|Nidah was saved, and its saviour rewarded.
Description: 据说有七个人试图将不朽普及.
LevelDescriptionText: 10|Begin your quest in London~20|Seek Isery, on the Isle of Cats~30|Seek the Fierce Philanthropist, at Port Carnelian~35|Search the cities beneath the zee for the Fierce Philanthropist's husband~40|Find the Fierce Philanthropist's husband at Low Barnet, near London~50|Ask Lytton about the Seven Against Nidah~60|Find Mariam, deep in Scrimshander's ivory Archives~200|With Mariam, plan the conquest of Nidah~70|Restore the Seven Against Nidah~300|Seven years pass...~1000|Seven Conquered Nidah~2000|One Conquered Nidah~3000|Nidah stands, and you were rewarded with a kingdom
Name: 志向:  死亡不再统御四方

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Find a way to defeat the Presbyter's armies.~0|You have begun a scheme to defeat the Presbyter's armies.
Description: 你如何击败长老议会无穷的军队?
Name: 志向:  尼达的军队

ChangeDescriptionText: 10|You are searching for Lytton.
Description: 搜寻水下城市来寻找暴躁的慈善家失踪的丈夫.
Name: 志向:  寻找立顿

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Seek Lytton in Aigul, the City of Regrets.
Description: 暴躁的慈善家的丈夫在爱古吗?
Name: 志向:  寻找立顿: 爱古

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Seek Lytton in Anthe, the City of Flowers.
Description: 暴躁的慈善家的丈夫去过安忒吗?
Name: 志向:  寻找立顿: 安忒

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Seek Lytton in Dahut, the City of Peace.
Description: 暴躁的慈善家的丈夫在达哈吗?
Name: 志向:  寻找立顿: 达哈

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Seek Lytton in Hideaway, the City of Refuge.
Description: 暴躁的慈善家的丈夫在隐逸之地吗?
Name: 志向:  寻找立顿: 隐逸之地

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Seek Lytton in Nook, the City of Freedom.
Description: 暴躁的慈善家在旮旯吗?
Name: 志向:  寻找立顿: 旮旯

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Seek Lytton in Scrimshander, the City of Rememberance.
Description: 暴躁的慈善家的丈夫在骨雕馆吗?
Name: 志向:  寻找立顿: 骨雕馆

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Seek Lytton in Wrack, the City of Delights.
Description: 暴躁的慈善家的丈夫去船墟了吗?
Name: 志向:  寻找立顿: 船墟

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|The Seven need a fleet-captain.~5|The Seven have found their fleet-captain.
Description: 谁来统治七人团的舰队
LevelDescriptionText: 1|You have yet to recruit someone~5|Arik
Name: 志向:  司令

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|The Seven require a financier.~5|The Seven have found their financier.
Description: 谁来为重振的七人团提供资金对抗尼达?
LevelDescriptionText: 1|You have yet to recruit one~5|The Fierce Philanthropist
Name: 志向:  金主

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|The Seven require a guide.~5|The Seven have found their guide.~3|Isery, who dwells on the Isle of Cats, may replace Lorenzo.
Description: 谁来带队前往尼达?
LevelDescriptionText: 1|You have yet to recruit someone~5|Isery~3|Seek Isery, on the Isle of Cats
Name: 志向:  向导

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|The Seven require a healer.~5|The Seven have found their healer.
Description: 谁来保护七人团对抗长老议会的无尽危险?
LevelDescriptionText: 1|You have yet to recruit someone~10|The Banded Prince~5|Rosina~3|If Rosina cannot help, perhaps the Banded Prince of the Carnelian Coast can replace her
Name: 志向:  治愈者

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|The Seven require a Propagandist.~5|The Seven have found their Propogandist.~3|Perhaps a Voracious London Diplomat could replace Bourdain.
Description: 谁来负责宣传?
LevelDescriptionText: 1|You have yet to recruit someone~5|Bourdain, or what is left of him~3|If you cannot retrieve Bourdain, a Voracious London Diplomat may make a suitable replacement~10|The Voracious Diplomat
Name: 志向:  宣传官

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Find a way to reach Nidah.~0|You have begun a scheme to reach Nidah.
Description: 尼达静静地立在古大陆的深处, 在丛林, 沙漠以及平原的远方. 你们如何到达那里?
Name: 志向:  去往尼达之路

ChangeDescriptionText: 7|The Seven Against Nidah are reformed.~1|You have recruited someone to the Seven.
Description: 你必须重振对抗尼达的七人团.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|One of Seven~2|Two of Seven~3|Three of Seven~4|Four of Seven~5|Five of Seven~6|Six of Seven~7|Seven of Seven
Name: 志向:  七人团, 重振

ChangeDescriptionText: 5|The Seven have found their commander.~1|The Seven need a commander.~3|Perhaps you can convince Batuk to rejoin the Seven.
Description: 谁来指挥七人团的军队?
LevelDescriptionText: 1|You have yet to recruit someone~5|Batuk~3|Convince Batuk to rejoin the Seven
Name: 志向:  士兵

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Find a way to breach Nidah's walls.~0|You have begun a scheme to breach Nidah's walls.
Description: 那城墙比女王的宫殿还高, 比无畏舰的长度还厚, 是黑色的玄武石建造的. 你要怎么摧毁它?
Name: 志向:  尼达的城墙

Description: 很幸运, 它正在睡.
Name: 你身上一个不显眼的额外眼睛

Description: 一名船员的梦, 在他的船长被黑女士带走之后剩下来的.
Name: 她心脏的黑色轮廓

Description: 现在你能离近看, 他看起来像是一张新纸上沾了一些... 咖啡味道的东西?
Name: 有些象古物的藏宝图

Description: 一份经过公正的拷贝静静地躺在 贝斯波恩 & 福林皮尔斯法律咨询中心的保险库里.另外一份,则由大巴扎保管. [这将会确认你的下一名船长能接管你的住所,还有你存在那里的所有遗产.]
Name: An Ironclad Will

Description: 这不会治愈敏锐的军医, 但是也许这能让她撑更长时间.
Name: 一个不太可能的综合治疗方法

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You have an Unprepossessing Mass.
Description: 一团正在滴下液体的可怕有机物,从你不愿去想的那些地方拿出来的.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|You have an Unprepossessing Mass
Name: 不讨人喜欢的团块

Description: 确实是死人, 你仔细检查过.
Name: 生物学展示柜

Description: 从船长的职责里解脱的珍贵的一晚. 你会怎么度过? [你每次回到伦敦都会得到这样的一夜.]
Name: 另一天: 空闲的一夜

ChangeDescriptionText: 0|Your business with the Alarming Scholar is concluded, for now.~1|The Alarming Scholar has invited you to call on her (him?) at the University
Description: 深海学院题头的信纸. 他想和你谈谈.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|The Alarming Scholar has invited you to call on her (him?)
Name: 另一天: 令人惊恐的学者的信

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Someone wants to sign on!~0|You have no more recruits for the moment.
Description: 有人想上船!
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Someone wants to sign on!
Name: 另一天: 新船员?

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|The Blind Bruiser attends to business on the dock.~0|The Blind Bruiser has departed.
Description: 盲眼壮汉想要说些什么.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|The Blind Bruiser attends to business on the dock
Name: 另一天: 盲眼壮汉来访

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Skulls whisper~11|Bones rattle~31|Shadows flicker~41|Stories end~51|Hearts falter~61|Empires crumble~21|Flesh fails~71|Light dims~81|Love dies~91|Dreams lie~100|Memories deceive
LevelDescriptionText: 1|The remains of countless stories surround you
Name: 另一天: 遗骨和可怕的故事

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|The Parliament of Flies is open for business~5|The Calvary Doctrine is open for business~10|The Gesundheit Conspiracy is open for business~15|The Expulsus is open for business
Description: 赶走旧法则, 迎进新法则.
Name: 另一天: 钢铁共和国的日子

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Horrors walk~11|Darkness coils~21|Dreams wait~31|Stone drops~41|Echo, echo...~51|Light flares~61|Wind gusts~91|Hearts pound~92|A child screams~81|Silence...silence~94|Pits gape~71|Shadows flicker~95|Still water~96|Distant laughter~97|Scuffed footsteps~98|Pale fungus~93|Spiders scuttle~99|Memories...~100|(Don't look)
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Something's out there
Name: 另一天: 黑暗中的秽物

ChangeDescriptionText: 10|Shrieks and chitters...~20|Eyes in the undernight...~30|Spreading ripples...~40|Swags of hanging fungus...~50|Fat white mosquitoes...~60|Shrieking cockatoos...~70|Sulphurous stirrings...~80|A dribble of sticky rain...~90|A moss-furred boat-skeleton...~1|Black and stinking mud...~100|A soft phosphorescence...
Description: 航行到足够深的地方, 你会找到些有趣的东西.
LevelDescriptionText: 0|You've returned from the swamps!
Name: 另一天: 在沼泽中航行

Description: 也许有报酬在等着你.
Name: 另一天: 海盗的愉快

ChangeDescriptionText: 0|The Rose-Market has concluded, for now.~1|The Rose-Market bustles on Roser's Wharf. Who will be there today?
Description: 一个坐落在种玫人码头的人头攒动的市场, 专门面向收集者和古怪的人营业.
Name: 另一天: 玫瑰市场

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Something has changed in the Neath
Description: 你在海中度过的时间会改变你...还有伦敦.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Ever-changing
Name: 另一天: 时间能治愈一切

Description: 你得到的奖励在伦敦等着你. 回到你的住处领取.
Name: 另一天: 为了胜利, 为了战利品

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You are at the edge of the Citadel.~2|You are in the second tangle of tunnels.~3|You are in the third tangle of tunnels.~5|You are in the fifth tangle of tunnels.~6|You are in the sixth tangle of tunnels.~7|You are in the seventh tangle of tunnels.~8|You have reached the Citadel's root...~9|You have entered the Citadel's root...~4|You have reached the mid-point of the Citadel
Description: 下面有什么?
Name: 另一天: 深入破碎城堡的探险

ChangeDescriptionText: 0|Visitors have departed.~1|Someone would like to call on you at your Lodgings.
Description: 有人会拜访你的住所.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Someone would like to call on you at your Lodgings.
Name: 另一天: 访客

Description: 你了解了些关于曾林的静谧小径的事情. [提升到7才能找到你正在找的东西.]
Name: 另一天:那些树木

AvailableAt: 安忒
ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Your tongue is transparent and its edges are perfectly squared.
Description: 你的舌头是一块软钻石吗? 你的言语闪光吗? 你的言语锐利吗?
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Hard-tongued
Name: 安忒: 晶化舌头

AvailableAt: 只有长时间在安忒活动才会让你得到安忒人的能力.
Description: 你是否使用晶化来强化特别的技能?
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Mirrors~2|Pages~3|Hearts~4|Iron
Name: 安忒: 安忒的优势

Description: 一份爱情小说被安忒最好的意识修订.
Name: 安忒: 安忒的浪漫

AvailableAt: 安忒
ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Your respiration slows. Your exhalations are cold and dry.
Description: 你的肺是一块中空闪耀的晶洞吗?
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Barb-lunged
Name: 安忒: 肺之刺

AvailableAt: 在安忒培养.
ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You can now take on a single sharpness.~2|You can now take on another sharpness.~7|You can hold seven sharpnesses. Seven is the maximum.
Description: 你可以忍受多少晶化?
LevelDescriptionText: 1|You can go sharp, but only in one area.~2|You can be sharp in two ways.~3|Triple sharpness will not harm you. You can endure it.~4|Quadruple sharpness? Yes. Why not? Half of you is sharp, but will you mind?~5|You are capable of being more than half crystal.~6|Six. Six sharpnesses.~7|Total
Name: 安忒: 晶化容量

AvailableAt: 在安忒寻找.
ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You crackle when you move.
Description: 你是透明的吗? 你向世界展示了你的连接吗?
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Transparent
Name: 安忒: 表皮的清澈

AvailableAt: 在安忒获取.
ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Anthe is now haunted by Conflagranti.~2|Anthe is now free of Conflagranti.
Description: 罗西娜的观众们现在已经被燃魂病感染, 并开始在此徘徊.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Conflagranti wander the chambers of Anthe, suffering from and trying to spread their animescence.~2|Anthe has been cleansed of Conflagranti.
Name: 安忒: 燃灵团

AvailableAt: 在安忒的第一个房间获取
ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Your liver has turned to a crystalline sieve.
Description: 你的肝脏将不受任何影响.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Crystal-livered
Name: 安忒: 肝脏结晶化

AvailableAt: 在可汗的荣耀开始, 在安忒继续.
ChangeDescriptionText: 10|You are retrieving information from Anthe for Khan's Glory.~20|You are searching Anthe's sharp-tongued chambers for information to return to Khan's Glory.~30|You are returning information to Khan's Glory from Anthe.~40|You have reliably informed Khan's Glory about a matter in Anthe.
Description: 为可汗的荣耀准备的报告
LevelDescriptionText: 10|You are retrieving information from Anthe for Khan's Glory.~15|You are searching Anthe's sharp-tongued chambers for information to return to Khan's Glory.~20|You are returning information to Khan's Glory from Anthe.~30|You have reliably informed Khan's Glory about a matter in Anthe.
Name: 安忒: 大量情报

AvailableAt: 安忒
ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Your dimensions do not change, only your substance.
Description: 身体的任何一部分都可以变晶化.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Bristle-groined
Name: 安忒: 腹股沟的晶化

AvailableAt: 安忒提供水晶化的机会.
Description: 你已经变晶化了多少部分?
Name: 安忒: 晶化的数量

AvailableAt: 安忒
LevelDescriptionText: 10|Carrying an exile back to Polythreme~20|Delivered an exile back to Polythreme~5|Encountered a Polythreme Exile who was sharp in lung and bone
Name: 安忒: 碎心国的放逐者

AvailableAt: 安忒
ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You've seen the outer chambers of Anthe and learned what the place is.
Description: 你在安忒外室游荡.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|You've seen the outer chambers of Anthe and learned what the place is.
Name: 安忒: 初步探访

AvailableAt: 在安忒和罗欣娜互动.
Description: 你对罗欣娜了解多少?
Name: 安忒: 与罗西娜相识

Description: 她从燃魂病中活了下来?
LevelDescriptionText: 10|Recovered~20|Deceased
Name: 安忒: 罗西娜的命运

AvailableAt: 罗欣娜的健康取决于安忒发生的事件.
Description: 罗西娜距离因燃魂病而死还有多远?
LevelDescriptionText: 0|Extremely ill~3|Heating quickly~6|Feverish~9|A bit warm~10|Almost stable~17|Nearly recovered~11|Showing signs of improvement~14|Almost cool
Name: 安忒: 罗西娜的健康

AvailableAt: 安忒
ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Your spleen is a hexagonal crystal.
Description: 来自安忒的第一内室.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Sharp-spleened
Name: 安忒: 晶化脾

AvailableAt: 安忒
ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Your skeleton has sharpened and clarified.
Description: 你的颅骨足够锐利吗?
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Spiny
Name: 安忒: 晶化之骨

Description: 用珊瑚雕刻, 和珊瑚之源有着相同的脉动.
Name: 月蓝色的棋子

Description: 税务员移除了其中可能引起争议的部分, 然后在书的封皮上盖上了海关的印章.
Name: 已审查浪漫小说

Description: 最后的秘密?
Name: 最后: 盐神的歌

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You spoke your burning name, at last~2|You sacrificed your mortal past~3|You've unravelled all your fates~4|In the Pillared City, Salt's Song waits~5|You gave the Exile to disgrace~6|The Exile earned a kind of grace~7|The Exile turned aside her face~8|Do you recall how we came to that place?
Description: 你已经很接近了.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|You spoke your burning name, at last~2|You sacrificed your mortal past~4|In the Pillared City, Salt's Song waits~3|You've unravelled all your fates~5|You gave the Exile to disgrace~6|The Exile earned a kind of grace~7|The Exile turned aside her face~8|Do you recall how we came to that place?
Name: 最后: 那个极限

Description: 一大块从天而降的陨铁, 一辆手推车的大小. 在它的侧面闪着符文的火花.一个星星的种子在它里面. 它在看着你.你确定你知道你要拿这东西来做什么吗?
Name: 被唤醒封印的红科技

Description: 谁从流过梦境的河流的堤岸上扯下了这些?
Name: 一捆帕布拉亚麻

Description: 他烹饪的海鲜能让皇帝落泪.
Name: Bandaged Chef-Paramount

AvailableAt: He may sometimes be found in the Tomb-Colonies
Description: 他对海鲜烹饪很有野心. 而且是巨大的野心.
Name: 缠满绷带的海鲜厨师

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You are seen.
Description: 你被看见了.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|You are seen
Name: Beheld

Description: 波浪在你头顶之上.
Name: Below

Description:
"就像一道横梁跨越海泽,
横跨所有黄金年代!" [一件对寻找敌人非常有用的设备.]
Name: 闪耀的灯晶灯

Description: 多么敏锐的小蘑菇！
Name: Blemmigan Gallivanter

Description: 如静谧本身一般柔软.
Name: 一卷蜘蛛丝

Description: 从硫磺公约中搜集的情报,那是地狱的流亡政府.
Name: Brimstone Buzzings

AvailableAt: Sometimes available for hire in London.
Description: 她曾给将军们看病,也曾和军队一起行军. 千万别惹她.
Name: 敏感的军医

Description: 你选择加速.让我们看看他们能不能赶上这!
Name: 加速!

Description: 一种笨重但是货仓很大的船.
Name: Caligo-class Merchant Cruiser

Description: 吞噬发动机的排放物,确保你的发动机不会在全速前进状态下爆炸.同时能略微增加敌人忽视你的几率.
Name: 卡米努斯验证型 贪婪消烟装置

Description: "這是個怪獸,你難道不這麼認為嗎?" 一件强力的鱼雷发射器.
Name: 卡米努斯验证型 '幻想猛兽'

Description: 引擎困住了一头怒吼的巨兽.
Name: 卡米努斯验证型 '强袭'

Description: 不要提起它.
Name: 卡米努斯验证型 '__亡国度'

Description: "卡米努斯试验场: 我们一直爱着你." 这件强力的武器可以轻松撕开海兽的防护.
Name: 卡米努斯验证型 竭心者

Description: "卡米努斯试验场: 靠后点站." 一件野蛮而令人恐惧的武器.
Name: 卡米努斯验证型 地狱收割机

Description: 把老鼠送到需要老鼠的地方, 完全气动. [在战斗中, 这能把法布尔鼠技工送到损伤位置进行快速修复.]
Name: 卡米努斯验证型 气动老鼠传输机

Description: 这个记号表明你安装了火炮.
Name: 火炮

Description: 你最终会移开视线. [如果你已经订立了遗嘱,你能把这个东西变成留给后继者的遗物.]
Name: 迷人的财宝

Description: 用蜡层层密封.
Name: 一瓶原始的尖叫

Description: 在海底发现的黑暗之物. 你可以将其送到骨雕馆.
Name: 一货仓回答

Description: 你的货舱安全吗?
Name: 保险货仓

AvailableAt: Sometimes available for hire in London.
Description: 柔和的嗓音和一点点神秘. 她能看见多少?
Name: 玛瑙港的放逐者

Description: 格林菲尔德蘑菇园最棒的一批.
Name: 一桶蘑菇酒

Description: Increase this to 50 before Mouse reaches 1...
Name: Cat: Getting Warmer

Description: 一位切除专家.
Name: 覆叶的继承人

AvailableAt: 可以在许多覆叶的继承人能够进行手术的地方找到.
Description: 一个覆叶的继承人切下的部分.
Name: 覆叶的纪念品

AvailableAt: 这可以在卡米安运河等待区找到.
Description: 覆叶的继承人在卡米安船闸进行了手术吗?
Name: 覆叶的手术: 卡米安船闸

AvailableAt: 这个治疗会在伊瑞暮发生.
Description: 覆叶的继承人在伊瑞暮进行了手术吗?
Name: 覆叶的手术: 伊瑞暮

Description: 你让覆叶的继承人使邮差不再是邮差.
Name: 覆叶的手术: 农西奥

AvailableAt: Port Carnelian
Description: 覆叶的继承人进行了手术吗?
Name: 覆叶的手术: 玛瑙港

Description: 你好,我不會惹麻煩的.
Name: 粘土人, 标记去往伦敦

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Bound for Gaider's Mourn.~5|A second request.~10|Bound for the Cumaean Canal.~15|A final request.~20|Bound for Khan's Heart.~25|An Agreement enforced.~100|You refused to carry him any farther.~50|The August Travel-Writer - one Robert F. Harris - nearly blew up your ship and zubmarine.	~75|The August Travel-Writer - one Robert F. Harris - failed in his bomb plot against you.
Description: 看起来威严的旅行作家去到哪里, 哪里就会发生非常引人注意的事情.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Bound for Gaider's Mourn~5|A second request~10|Bound for the Cumaean Canal~15|A final request~20|Bound for Khan's Heart~25|The August Travel-Writer enforced an Agreement	~50|The August Travel-Writer - one Robert F. Harris - nearly blew up your ship and zubmarine	~75|The August Travel-Writer - one Robert F. Harris - failed to blow up your ship and zubmarine	~100|You refused to carry the August Travel-Writer any farther
Name: Closing Chapters

Description: 多愁善感而且沉溺于过去, 就像靛紫被琥珀囚禁一样,它被靛紫束缚着.哀悼着那些逝去的心灵.
Name: 巨大的锚爪海胆

Description: 大多数情况下它很平静. 偶尔, 它会很野蛮.
Name: 睡不醒的雪貂

Description: 提供一些低程度的防护来防止税务官检查出你的违禁品.
Name: 隐蔽的区域

Description: 你的违禁品在搜查官的搜查下有多安全?
Name: 隐藏违禁品

Description: 严格上来讲, 这根本不应该卖给平民的船只, 但是海军的纪律最近越来越松散了.
Name: 卡特洛尔 & 哈瑟萨奇 海军特供

Description: "不要再做這件事了." 卡特洛尔 & 哈瑟萨奇公司的新型号.
Name: 卡特洛尔 & 哈瑟萨奇 '谴责者型'

Description: 对那些跟屁虫很有用.
Name: 卡特洛尔 & 哈瑟萨奇公司 '挫折型'

Description: 这能制造最大规模的爆炸. 不是你所想要的优雅兵器, 但是它能制造最强烈的爆炸. [威严型是只能向前射击的火炮: 其他的是鱼雷和鱼叉类武器.]
Name: 卡特洛尔 & 哈瑟萨奇公司 '威严型'

Description: 1到3号不能在一般的公司里见到, 但是这的确是件强力而有效的兵器.
Name: 卡特洛尔 & 哈瑟萨奇公司 '蝎狮 No.4'

Description: 这个设备使用了一种听起来让人难以置信的荒诞方法运行. 然而,它确实可以,让你发射鱼雷.
Name: 卡特洛尔 & 哈瑟萨奇公司 炸药气动鱼雷筒

Description: "我們將密切關注." 这件武器的威力令人赞叹.
Name: 卡特洛尔 & 哈瑟萨奇公司 '耻辱型'

Description: 这些曾经是诗人,谋杀犯或者牧师... 或者是船长. 这个箱子上印着海关的标识.
Name: 一箱卓越的人类灵魂

Description: 叮当作响, 发着微光, 从中传来哀求.
Name: 一箱人类灵魂

Description: 你的船上有多少水手?
Name: 船员

AvailableAt: 这个能力可以在达哈或者其他什么地方获取.
Description: 看穿溺亡者幻术的能力.
Name: 达哈: 明目

AvailableAt: 通过在达哈的互动提升.
Description: 你对达哈之美的沉迷深度.
Name: 达哈: 沉溺

AvailableAt: 在达哈进展, 或者在有什么事情等待你的时候离开或回来.
Description: 你在达哈度过的时间?
Name: 达哈: 逗留时长

AvailableAt: 在船墟开始这个故事, 在达哈继续.
Description: 你被要求找到一名在达哈被囚禁的人.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Asked to seek and free a prisoner in Dahut~10|Freed a prisoner of Dahut~20|Delivered a prisoner of Dahut to Rosegate~30|Reported back to the Composer at Wrack that the Dahut Prisoner was set free~2|Begun asking about a prisoner in Dahut~15|Brought a Dahut Prisoner to visit her friend in Wrack~3|Saw a prisoner in the Crypt
Name: 达哈: 寻找一名达哈的囚犯

Description: 照耀令汝等枯萎之地,護佑汝等不受灼燒.黎明机真的能指挥阳光? 况且,你真的想要它这么做吗?
Name: 黎明的法则

Description: 无法送达的信件.
Name: 死去的邮件

Description: [把这个带到文登湾的船坞来换一艘船.]
Name: 蒸汽游艇契约书

Description: 从巴扎上切下的一小块东西, 从合法的角度看, 这是属于你的.
Name: Deeds to the Cladery Heart

Description: 地下世界最伟大的探险家, 至少她自己是这么认为的.把她和她的保镖带到手掌帝国.
Name: 令人愉快的女冒险家

Description: 这些信件曾经无法递送,但是现在信封上有了新的地址.
Name: 可以被递送的信件

Description: 现在他有了目标.
Name: 坚定的医生

Description: 这些淡黄色东西的本质不甚明朗, 不过它们不太可能是恶魔的遗骨这件事倒是很确定. 它们通常保存在密封的小罐子里,也许会被某些人用作弹药.
Name: 恶魔骨骰子

Description: 他曾经相信过一些事情.
Name: 幻想破灭了的医生

Description: 它确实有锋利的爪子; 上面有吓人的钩状物; 但是现在它看起来并不想用它的爪子.
Name: 温顺的真菌虫

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You have despoiled a sacred place.
Description: 你踏入了圣地.
Name: 毁灭: 寒霜城的核心

Description: 最敏锐的头脑通常也是最脆弱的.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Rambling
Name: 毁灭: 学者的疯狂行为

Description: 你想要从莲花海中的监狱里救出一名囚犯...
Name: 毁灭: 智慧监狱的警告

Description:
'怪物猎人能找到并筛选出那些现实中的恐怖生物.她已经屠灭了深渊中发出光的生物, 在对海泽盛宴的回忆中吃掉了它的血肉, 用它的尸骨做成了武器.她曾经是个人类.' 
但是这个怪物猎人已经为辉煌的结局做好了准备. 黑色逐日者正在等待着.
Name: 濒死的怪物猎人

Description: 一个无知的年代永远无法否定的可怕而大胆的猜测. [如果你出售了这个,你就会发现它难以取代.]
Name: Dread Surmise

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Bound for Venderbight.~5|Bound for Polythreme.~50|Committed to the Royal Bethlehem.~10|She knows what she must do.~100|Into the zee
Description: 未决的打捞者想要航向远方找到她.
LevelDescriptionText: 5|Bound for Polythreme~1|Bound for Venderbight~50|You committed the Unsettled Salvager to the Royal Bethlehem~10|The Unsettled Salvager wants to dive to meet Lady Black again. You could let her, or you could try to find help for her~100|The Unsettled Salvager dived and did not return.
Name: 关于女士的梦

AvailableAt: 某些情况下可以在达哈获取.
Description: 来自深处关于崇拜与爱慕的歌.
Name: 溺亡者赞歌

AvailableAt: 在达哈找到.
Description: 关于暗流和泥沙的歌.
Name: 溺亡者情歌

AvailableAt: 在达哈用一些代价获取.
Description: 关于孤立和归属的歌, 同样歌唱了伟大之物和人性.
Name: 和声溺亡者之歌

Description: 仍然像溺亡者的指尖那样冰冷...
Name: 溺者珍珠

Description: 回声是巴扎使用的货币; 并且, 因此, 伦敦也是用它作为自己的货币.
Name: Echo

Description: 一个破旧不堪布满锈迹的引擎至少可以确保你的船航行在大致正确的方向上.
Name: 古旧的复合式引擎

Description: 一个有着宏伟顶冠的鹦鹉,只会说那些它认为足够优秀的挽诗. 它的内心一定十分悲伤.
Name: 唱挽歌的凤头鹦鹉

Description: 这是一块黎明机器喷出或加工出的东西, 它的运动并未随着离开黎明机器而停止.
Name: 黎明元素

Description: 手掌帝国为你安排了和钢铁共和国进行氢气交易的相关事项.
Name: 手掌帝国: 地狱贸易协定

Description: 无论令人愉快的考古学家正在找什么,那一定是件很有价值的东西. 如果你愿意帮忙,你也许能从中分得一杯羹.
Name: 手掌帝国:令人愉快的考古行动
手掌帝国: 探索灰烬地峡

Description: 手掌帝国最神圣的岛屿, 无论任何阶层的猴子对这里都充满了尊敬.
Name: 手掌帝国: 探索过的水源岛

Description: 手掌帝国唯一的人类定居点
Name: 手掌帝国: 探索过的炉烬岛

Description: 奇怪的手掌帝国无情的心脏
Name: 手掌帝国: 探索过的君主岛

Description: 你正在圣所之中.
Name: 手掌帝国: 探索第一任皇帝的圣所

Description: 你发现了手掌帝国的机遇
Name: 手掌帝国: 猴子的生意

Description: 它不会轻易表现出来的.
LevelDescriptionText: 2|Your ticket on board the Empire of Hands' Zeppelin. Hopefully it was worth it.~1|The Monkey Emperor's price is high, but if you want to steal his prize...
Name: 手掌帝国: 猴子皇帝的喜爱

Description: 这个. 永不. 发生.
Name: 手掌帝国: 尊严的任务

Description: 好吧. 你觉得这挺好的.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|The Flying Monkey~2|The Other Name
Name: 手掌帝国: 被飞艇拒绝

AvailableAt: 如果你胆敢使用这个, 那就把它带去伦敦
Description: 一箱煽动性的文件.仅仅是揭示出他们中有的人正在秘密对抗法律 .
Name: 手掌帝国: 猴子皇帝的愤怒

Description: 手掌帝国将需要它去它要去的地方.
Name: 手掌帝国: 飞艇 - 燃料

Description: 灵魂的帝国需要灵魂来抬升它那些受过诅咒的居民.
Name: 手掌帝国: 飞艇 - 灵魂

Description: 手掌帝国将来的旅途上会需要这些的.
Name: 手掌帝国: 飞艇 - 补给

Description: 最终一个孩子会解出它...
Name: 手掌帝国: 汉诺塔的剩余步数
手掌帝国: 财宝谷 X
手掌帝国: 财宝谷 Y

Description: 你的灵魂居住于手掌帝国
Name: 手掌帝国: 未经许可的灵魂走私

AvailableAt: 通过交易, 补给飞艇, 或者取悦变化无常的圣灵猿提升.
Description: 你现在站在猴子的宫殿前.
Name: 手掌帝国: 野林中的地位

Description: 内置了镜子矩阵的匣子: 一个不可思议的设备,它被用来捕获阳光.
Name: 空的捕光镜匣

AvailableAt: 她在伦敦外的远方狩猎, 既针对其他的海盗, 也针对那些旅行太远的旅者.
Description: 你在海泽里有对手了.
LevelDescriptionText: 20|You have once again defeated the Pirate-Poet~30|You have dined with the Pirate-Poet~40|You have forged a rivalry with the Pirate-Poet~90|You have abandoned the Pirate-Poet to the zee~99|The Pirate-Poet has written her last verse~50|You have reached a rapport with the Pirate-Poet~10|You have defeated the Pirate-Poet~0|You have heard of the Pirate-Poet
Name: 遭遇海盗诗人

Description: 有些东西发生了严重的错误.
Name: 引擎过载

Description: 海兽们能够击沉人们之前建造过的所有船只.末日级是为了打破这个惯例而建造的.
Name: 毁灭级无畏舰

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Everything is probably perfectly all right.
Description: 许多事情发生了, 但是可能没什么值得担心的.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Don't worry
Name: Everything is Probably Perfectly All Right

Description: 在玛瑙港的隐蔽工房将其提升至 100 来将你的船变形为潜艇.
LevelDescriptionText: 1| You can trade Zee-Ztories, Stygian Ivory, Outlandish Artefacts, or Extraordinary Implications to increase this.
Name: 实验与修改

Description: 怎么可能有这样的一件东西? 除了你还有谁能明白它的意思?
Name: 非凡的暗示

AvailableAt: 这个东西可以在伦敦的遗忘区找到. 魔术师会为你打开这个区域.
Description: 眼眶被厚厚的骨板覆盖, 就好像是要把眼眶隐藏或保护起来. 它们摸起来又光滑又冰冷. 靛紫的光从它颚骨的缝隙处溢出.
Name: 无眼骷髅头

Description: 你见过了覆叶继承人的父亲.
Name: 相熟于覆叶继承人的父亲

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You've established a useful relationship with a coffee-house in Vienna.~2|You've sold coffee to your contact in Vienna.
Description: 你和维也纳的咖啡屋有了互助的关系.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|You've established a useful relationship with a coffee-house in Vienna.~300|Your relationship with the Café Ferstel has ended.
Name: 声望: 一滴黑暗

Description: 无政府主义者最可怕的对手.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|An Understanding~2|A Particular Understanding
Name: 声望: 办公桌前的绅士

Description: 你交了个汗国的朋友.
Name: 声望: 一个白锡马头

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You accepted the proposal~2|You agreed to smuggle souls from London to Mt Palmerston~101|You refused the proposal~3|You delivered souls to Mt Palmerston~5|You've been asked to pick something up...~4|You were paid~6|You've been given a task...
Description: 一个阴影中的人给了你一个提议.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|You accepted the proposal~2|You agreed to smuggle souls from London to Mt Palmerston~3|You delivered souls to Mt Palmerston~4|You were paid~5|You've been asked to pick something up...~101|You refused the proposal~6|You were given a task...
Name: 声望: 一个商人的建议

Description: 你和切洛内特的海兽猎人成为了朋友.
Name: 声望: 一枚鲸骨护符

Description: 你为海军部服务过，他们不会忘记的。
Name: 声望: 海军的声望

Description: 你在海中探索来寻找秘密和其他的财富.
Name: 声望: 古文物收藏家

Description: 你送给雪豹部族的礼物给你带来了一点点好名声.
Name: 声望:雪豹的傲慢

Description: 你送给鲑鱼部族的礼物给你带来了一点点好名声.
Name: 声望: 鲑鱼的仁慈

Description: 在伦敦的屋顶上, 日历会谋划着终结法律的统治.
Name: 声望:日历会

Description: 每一桶里都有一百个梦.
Name: 一小桶囚徒之蜜

Description: 照明弹可以为你照亮你的敌人, 加速你的开火进程.
Name: 照明弹

AvailableAt: 在普朗蒂太太的码头供应商处购买.
Description: 我们犯了所有的错误. 如果那些错误能留在黑暗中多好.
Name: 狐火蜡烛

Description: 知识的一个碎片. [发现怪物和地点来获得碎片.足够数量的碎片可以合成秘密.]
Name: 碎片

Description: 煤, 从海泽中的峭壁上挖掘出来或者从地狱进口. [如果你用尽了燃料,你只能无助的漂泊在海上.]
Name: 燃料

Description: 她的眼睛很快就会孵化. 但是在那之前, 她想要工作.
Name: 眼睛即将孵化的工程师

Description: 只有切洛内特人对这个有食欲.
Name: 刚特极点:一桶腐肉

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You have been given a message.~2|You have delivered the message.
Description: 你被要求带信去加德的哀悼.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|You have been asked to deliver a message to Gaider's Mourn~2|You have delivered the message
Name: 刚特极点: 死者的信

ChangeDescriptionText: 3|Blood still obscures the truth.~2|A pattern is emerging.~1|You can see nothing in the viscera.~4|You are on the edge of a revelation.
Description: 浮现出的画.
Name: 刚特极点: 血与骨的秘密

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|The Redolent Fleshmerchant has requested 'meath' from the Gant Pole.~10|The Redolent Fleshmerchant is out of business.
Description: 如果有合适的调味料, 饥饿的人什么都能吃.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|The Redolent Fleshmerchant has requested 'meath' from the Gant Pole~10|The Redolent Fleshmerchant is out of business
Name: 刚特极点: 血肉交易

Description: 越过噬王者城堡的海域黑暗而宁静.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|The Sixth Witness asked you to visit the Gant Pole~2|You have the answer for the Sixth Witness at Kingeater's Castle~3|The Seventh Witness has looked East from Kingeater's Castle
Name: 刚特极点: 见证虚无

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You are learning the ways of haruspicy.
Description: 秘密被埋进了血与骨中.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|It is all just a mass of entrails to you~4|You have learned how the Fading Haruspex performs her rituals~5|Patterns begin to emerge~3|Your stomach no longer jumps at the thought of divination~2|You have seen a spark of the truth
Name: 刚特极点: 肠卜师的学徒

Description: 你正在探索这座道路曲折的迷宫.
Name: 刚特极点: 心之走廊

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You are performing haruspicy.
Description: 刀在你手中显得十分沉重.
Name: 刚特极点: 深入近死者

ChangeDescriptionText: 7|The beast is strong. Its blood pumps thick and hard.~6|The beast's body thrashes in agony.~5|The beast's blood blackens. Viscous. Oily.~4|The beast's pulse weakens. It has little time left.~3|The beast moans. It barely has the energy to quiver.~0|The beast is silent. Its pain is over.~2|The beast shakes, mewling for the end.~1|The beast's final heartbeats pound their last.
Description: 这个生物已经没多少剩下的部分了.
Name: 刚特极点: 最后呼吸

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You continue walking through the Gant Pole.~0|You have left the Gant Pole's ventricles.
Description: 每一步都引领你通向结局.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|The echo of silver writing glimmers in the darkness. "IT TORE OUT THE HEART. THE SHAME REMAINED."~2|A scowling pirate cleans his teeth with a dagger. The Gant Pole's depths are a fine place to hide, for those who can find it.~3|The tunnel twists into three directions. You lick your finger. The slight breeze guides your feet.~4|A gust of fetid air rushes through the tunnel. The heart shudders for a moment.~6|Slivers of calcified heart rain down from the cracked ventricle roof.~7|This ventricle narrows to a tight gap. Fossilised fat deposits crack under your feet.~8|The light of your candle flickers. In the darkness behind you, footsteps.~9|A group of Old Zailors sits in a circle, tearing strips off a recently arrived whale with their rotten teeth.~10|One of the Fading Haruspex's disciples scurries past, arms weighed down with supplies from deeper in the Gant Pole.~11|A gentle hum guides your feet forwards. Your eyes feel heavy. Somewhere here is a place you can sleep. You have earned your rest. There is no need to awaken.~12|You brush your hand against the rippled edges of the tunnel. Another ventricle. Was it flesh before it was stone?~13|You pass an encampment of zailors. They stare at you, refusing to talk. You move onwards and deeper into the Heart.~14|Water drips from a crack in the roof. You taste it. Stale and stagnant. Brine aftertaste. Still better than thirst.~15|In the distance, someone whistles a zee-shanty. It might be you.~16|The echo of silver writing glimmers in the darkness. "REJOICE, FOR THE END ALWAYS COMES."~17|You pass a wall covered in chalk-malks. Whether they mark days, years, or something else, whoever made them has been here for a very long time.~18|For a moment, you see a glow in the distance. It fades as soon as you look up.~20|Every tunnel twists and turns. Is a little treasure really so much to ask for in such a grim place?~5|Down this tunnel, you pass one of the Old Zailors writing something on the wall. In the light, it is invisible. In the darkness, illegible.~19|You pass a shack made of hide. The owner sleeps inside, gently breathing despite the polished bone of his skeleton visible through the decay and great chunks of devoured flesh. He cackles to himself about something in his dream, rolls over, and begins to snore.
Name: 刚特极点: 迷失在黑暗中

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|The flesh reveals all.
Description: 肠卜者从近死的海兽内脏中拉出了它们.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|"There is a question waiting. It travelled in a ship long wreck’d. Find it."~2|"The beast is tethered - but not forever. Refuge comes to London." ~3|"They were seven and they shall be seven again. Their names may change but the number remains." ~4|"The names of the heirs to Nidah will begin with M, A, R, I - which is rebellion." ~5|"Beneath the waves, two cities live. They grow. They hunger."~6|"Beware Anthe. It will change you. You will be sharp, keen as a knife’s edge."~7|"The wound reopens; the flesh will not heal. Bring them your remorse." ~8|"They yearn for it: Liberty, Equality, Eternity."~9|"They are only mortal. They suffer too: Vitality, Infirmity, Fatality."~10|"The preacher travels to the bell tower. The bell, it- Oh god. That's horrid." ~11|"The one they fear waits in a pale cavern. The walls are carved with prophecies."~13|"The dream is great and ancient. It is fuelled by deeds of horror; none will have strength to deny it." ~14|"Wheels turn within wheels; a king yearns for your hand."~15|"One joins us below. The trespasser does not surface." ~16|"A question will not go unanswered indefinitely."~18|"The Salted will rise above the waves. They will find only their graves."~19|"An ancient beast wakes when the trespasser’s light pierces the abyss. The trespasser shall never know peace; only terror." ~20|"There shall be a new horizon. All shall know it - but the king’s city will witness it first." ~12|"The Soldier fled, and smothered himself in freedom."~17|"Freedom is fragile. The beast will wake."
Name: 刚特极点: 深处的预兆

ChangeDescriptionText: 0|The Gant Pole awaits its next weary beast.~1|A beast heads to the Gant Pole.
Description: 一个海兽去了刚特极点.
LevelDescriptionText: 2|Triskelegant~3|Beloved~4|Behemoustache~1|Thalatte
Name: 刚特极点: 一些东西的结局

Description: 她有她的答案. 该回到何方了.
Name: Gant Pole: The Fading Haruspex

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|The Haruspex fades a little more.~99|The Haruspex is no more.~90|The Haruspex has boarded your ship~95|The Haruspex has returned home~3|The Haruspex approaches her end.~4|The Haruspex prepares to breathe her last.
Description: 她的大限快到了.
LevelDescriptionText: 90|The Haruspex has returned home~99|The Haruspex has faded~1|The Haruspex clings to life a little longer~95|The Haruspex has returned home~3|The Haruspex is almost gone~4|The Haruspex prepares to breathe her last
Name: Gant Pole: The Fading Haruspex

Description: 并不是所有的海泽中的古物都会游泳.
Name: 刚特极点: 秘密水手据点

AvailableAt: Sometimes available for hire in London.
Name: 亲切的魔术师

Description: 一个从好战的豚鼠维亚家来的很有学者风度的生物,那里的贵族先知先觉地偷到了一艘蒸汽船,逃出了伦敦评论家即将锁上的笼子.  这很显然.
Name: 豚鼠侍者

Description: 装备并在海中使用它来挑战海盗诗人.
Name: 海盗之林

Description: 一桶非常小,但是有着剃刀般牙齿的蛇状鱼.
Name: 哈洛特鱼苗

Description: 这个记号表明你装备了鱼叉类武器.
Name: 鱼叉

AvailableAt: Sometimes available for hire in London.
Description: 认真, 博学, 有突然发出噪声的倾向.
Name: Haunted Doctor

Description: 鼓舞,治疗,防御. [有时这会对恐惧相关的判定有帮助.]
Name: 红心值

Description: 一件通过死亡传递的信件. [这会安全的放在你的住所里.]
Name: 继承物

Description: 这些既不生长在这个世界里也不生长在这个世界外.
Name: 赫斯珀里得斯苹果

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You are participating in the Silent Reel!~2|You are participating in the Hour of Our Reflection!~3|You are participating in the Rainbowing!
Description: 今晚怎么庆祝?
LevelDescriptionText: 1|The Silent Reel~2|The Hour of Our Reflection~3|The Rainbowing
Name: 隐逸之地: 庆祝节日

Description: 隐逸之地是个转折点. 有些东西很快会失去控制.
LevelDescriptionText: 100|The dwellers choose to believe that all's well~110|The dwellers refuse the truth~120|The dwellers are maintaining their belief that all's well~130|The dwellers don't want to acknowledge the truth~140|The dwellers are struggling to deny the truth~160|The dwellers cannot ignore the truth~150|The dwellers are beginning to accept the truth
Name: 隐逸之地: 决定隐逸之地的未来
隐逸之地: 隐逸地的难民

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|He has asked you to take him to Hideaway.~2|He has asked you to take him to the Salt Lions.
Description: 一个问题很多的人正在你的船上.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|He has asked you to take him to Hideaway~2|He has asked you to take him to the Salt Lions
Name: 隐逸之地: 不礼貌的调查员

ChangeDescriptionText: 40|You saved Arik's central control board.~50|You ensured that Hideaway will be well maintained for Arik.~20|You helped Arik power an alternator.~10|You helped the Sprightly Visionary set up an alternator.
Description: 他有着极为强烈而糟糕的希望.
LevelDescriptionText: 40|You saved Arik's central control board	~50|You ensured that Hideaway will be well maintained for Arik~20|You helped Arik power an alternator~10|You helped the Sprightly Visionary set up an alternator
Name: 隐逸之地: 愉快的梦想家的野心

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|The Sprightly Visionary has made his request.~2|Consigned to the zee.~3|Delivered.
Description: 他要求你揭露智慧监狱的典狱长, 并要求去隐逸之地.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|The Sprightly Visionary has made his request~2|Consigned to the zee~3|Accepted by the Governor
Name: 隐逸之地: 愉快的梦想家的请求

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You refused to answer the Impolite Investigator's question.~3|You gave the Impolite Investigator all he needed for an answer.~5|The Impolite Investigator was distressed by your answer.~10|There is a search for truth being conducted in Hideaway.~20|The Impolite Investigator has discovered a distressing truth about Hideaway.~50|The truth will be fought over during the Silent Reel.~40|It is a fact: Temtum will outgrow Hideaway, destroying the city. The Impolite Investigator wants to tell the people.~60|The truth will be fought over during the Hour of Our Reflection.~70|The truth will be fought over during the Rainbowing.~80|Something has given way.~90|The truth is that all's well in Hideaway. No one knows otherwise.~150|The truth is that Hideaway is doomed. The people have fled the city.~250|The truth has been agreed upon: all's well in Hideaway.~175|Temtum will be lonely.~275|At least Temtum will not be alone.
Description: 隐逸之地的居民们认识到了他们面临的状况吗?
LevelDescriptionText: 1|You refused to answer the Impolite Investigator's question~3|You gave the Impolite Investigator all he needed for an answer~5|The Impolite Investigator was distressed by your answer~10|There is a search for truth being conducted in Hideaway~20|The Impolite Investigator has discovered a distressing truth about Hideaway~50|The truth will be fought over during the Silent Reel~40|It is a fact: Temtum will outgrow Hideaway, destroying the city. The Impolite Investigator wants to tell the people~60|The truth will be fought over during the Hour of Our Reflection~70|The truth will be fought over during the Rainbowing~80|Something has given way~90|The truth is that all's well in Hideaway. No one knows otherwise~150|The truth is that Hideaway is doomed. The people have fled the city~250|The truth has been agreed upon: all's well in Hideaway
Name: 隐逸之地: 真相

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|The festival has begun!~5|The festival continues.~10|The festival will soon conclude.
Description: 尝试充分利用它.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|The festival has begun!~5|The festival continues~10|The festival will soon conclude
Name: 隐逸之地: 时间流逝

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|It will be more difficult to participate in the festivals of Hideaway for a while.
Description: 隐逸之地的居民不相信外来者.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|It will be more difficult to participate in the festivals of Hideaway for a while
Name: 隐逸之地: 对你的堤防

Description: 你有多少空间?
Name: 货仓

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You should look for somewhere to live.~0|You've found somewhere to live!
Description: 你需要找到其他地方居住.最好快一点.
Name: 无家可归!

Description: 你的船现在是什么形状?
Name: Hull

Description: 我们所有人都需要吃东西.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Replete~25|Fed~50|Peckish~100|Desperate~75|Ravenous
Name: 饥饿

Description: 吃掉那些深处潜伏生物的血肉, 你的眼睛会发生变化.
Name: 猎人之眼

Description: 你的猎物已经被征服, 但是这个剩了下来.
Name: 狩猎战利品

Description: 这件令人绝望, 精神错乱的设备会造成末日般的伤害.即使是最强大的海怪都难以从这种攻击中幸存,但是它只能发射一种东西: 怪物猎人. [你能在切洛内特和可汗之影找到他们,有时候他们也会在其他地方出现.]
Name: 黑色逐日者

AvailableAt: 这个选项暂时不可用! 但是未来它会开放.
Description: 这个选项暂时不可用! 但是未来它会开放.
Name: Impossible!

Description: 你已远远超过你的对手.
Name: 领先

Description: 死亡啊, 你的力量去了哪里? 到底去了哪里. 别惹老兵, 死亡.
Name: 不屈的军医

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|The Gnomic Gallivant now knows his target's face.
Description: 好说格言的寻乐者寻找知道了他的目标的长相.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|The Gnomic Gallivant now knows his target's face
Name: 来自卡米安运河的信息

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|The Gnomic Gallivant discovered the whereabouts of his target.
Description: 好说格言的寻乐者已经发现了他目标的行踪.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|The Gnomic Gallivant discovered the whereabouts of his target
Name: 来自钢铁和米斯里合作公司的情报

Description: 哦, 我说! 有的人会感兴趣的.
Name: 有趣的片段

ChangeDescriptionText: 2| Pulp-miners have been trading Nerveline to the Hempen Man.
Description: 囊块挖掘者已经把神经索交给了麻衣人.
Name: 调查旮旯: 神经紧张的人

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Who is this Hempen Man? What is his connection to the Maw quakes? Is he even a Nooker?
Description: 麻衣人是旮旯的居民吗? 他和震动有什么关系?
Name: 调查旮旯: 麻衣人

Description: 麻衣人造了个钻头. 它正在慢慢钻入大嘴.
Name: 调查旮旯: 糟糕的钻头

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Supplies are being diverted down the gullet. Why?
Description: 补给和机器被转移到了洞中.
Name: 调查旮旯: 失踪的补给

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|The Hempen Man advocates killing the Maw. The Nerveless are his followers. Do the children follow him too?
Description: 一群愤愤不平的年轻人加入了想要杀死大嘴的狂热者队伍
Name: 调查旮旯: 无力者

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Mrs Collier clearly knows something about the missing children.~2|Mrs Collier allowed the Hempen Man to take her charges, in return for a promise to slay the Maw.
Description: 失踪的旮旯的孩子们曾经住在这里.
Name: 调查旮旯: 孤儿院

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Your future investigations with the Heir will be easier.
Description: 你和覆叶的继承人正在找什么吗?
Name: 和覆叶的继承人一同调查

Description: "我是自己命运的主人: 我是自己灵魂的船长." [你现在处于无情模式, 除了游戏基础的自动保存之外没有其他的储存槽位.如果你切换到仁慈模式你将失去这枚印章.]
Name: 不可战胜之印章

Description: 毀滅. 提升你造成的伤害.
Name: 钢铁值

AvailableAt: Sometimes available for hire in London.
Description: 船上欢迎热情, 但是这样的特质似乎不太适合炮手.
Name: 桀骜不驯的炮手

Description: 国王的爪牙依旧控制着猫岛.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|You have accepted Isery's Patronage~4|Delivered the Scholar's Notes to your Patron~2|Smuggling red honey to the Alarming Scholar~3|Delivered your shipment to the Alarming Scholar~5|Conducting Experiments in red honey~6|A successful experiment!~7|A friend of King's Claw~101|Refused Isery's friendship. Or lost it.
Name: 猫岛: 伊瑟琳的赞助

Description: 她更喜欢人们称她为花园女士. 或者蔷薇就好.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Accepted Zaira's Patronage~2|Smuggling red honey to the Merchant Venturer~3|Delivered the shipment to the Merchant Venturer~4|Passed the Venturer's Message to Zaira~6|Made a sacrifice to the Rose Garden~7|A friend of Zaira~101|Refused Zaira's friendship. Or lost it.
Name: 猫岛: 铁笼女士的赞助

Description: 你参与了一件太过荒谬的事情,这件事情接近真正的非法.
Name: 猫岛: 走私红蜂蜜

Description: 一枚猫眼琥珀的胸针,还有一个警告.
LevelDescriptionText: 2|More "passing awareness" than notice, really~1|You are, almost entirely, beneath his notice~3|Your antics intrigue~5|You have his attention
Name: 猫岛: 海盗王的通知

Description: 确定他们的罪恶会把你引向他们那里. [司命共鸣管不会影响你躲藏的能力.]
Name: 司命共鸣管

Description: 这是...一个灵魂? 它十分苍白而明亮. 他们说,像这样的灵魂是一个奇怪神明的孢子.
Name: 司命之卵

Description: 它的双翅承载了几千年的记忆.其中只有一小部分是美好的记忆.
Name: 监护官霜蛾

Description: 没人能拥有梦之钥匙. 这件东西将很快到来.
Name: 梦之匙

AvailableAt: This is a placeholder for a storyline associated with a character throughline.
Description: This is a placeholder for a storyline associated with a character throughline.
Name: 面之匙

AvailableAt: This is not yet available.
Description: This element is not yet implemented.
Name: Key of Histories

Description: 你的王国会被人怎么称呼?
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Aestival~2|New London~3|Lastport~4|Freedom~5|Utopia Beneath~6|Sophia~7|Fiddler's Gold~11|Sanctuary~12|The Empire of Trees~8|Peachtree Isle~10|Head Office~9|B____r Off
Name: 王国: 一个名字

Description: 茶叶就是文明. 但是咖啡是革命. [在这达到 5之前, 你可以一直用咖啡豆提升你的价值.]
Name: 王国: 咖啡就是力量

Description: 你的财产正在增长.
Name: 王国: 财产

Description: 铭记这一天.
Name: 王国: 建立

Description: 阴谋也许会给你在这个国家生存下去的手段. [在它到达 5之前, 你一直可以用关键情报提升你的财产.]
Name: 王国: 知识就是力量

Description: 你的人口正在提升.
Name: 王国: 人口

Description: 用闪闪发光的战利品装点你的大厅.  [在它到达5之前, 你一直可以用工艺品提升财富.]
Name: 王国: 财富就是力量

ChangeDescriptionText: 3|The Disillusioned Doctor is now your viceroy.~2|The Indomitable Campaigner is now your viceroy.~1|The Genial Magician is now your viceroy.
Description: 你不在的时候,你需要一名管理者.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|The Genial Magician~2|The Indomitable Campaigner~3|The Disillusioned Doctor
Name: 王国: 你的总督

Description: 你什么都不用解释. 在潜艇方面, 你就是专家.
Name: 关于潜艇的知识

Description: 我们所有人,将来都会变成这样; 但是别太着急为他悲伤.
Name: 可悲的遗物

Description: 空间狭小而且结构脆弱, 但是非常敏捷而迅速.
Name: 烛台级快艇

Description: 加快呼吸并没有用. 头痛并未消退. 耳鸣不断, 再过一会就好了吗?
Name: 最后一口气

Description: "波阿狄西亞: 更強馬力,更低價格." 李德彼特&斯坦罗德公司能提供的最好产品,尽管通常情况下他们会偷工减料.
Name: 李德彼特&斯坦罗德公司 '波阿狄西亞'

Description: "畏惧她的利刃!" 李德彼特&斯坦罗德公司最可靠的一款,不用提太多. 允许你进行鱼叉攻击.
Name: 李德彼特&斯坦罗德公司 '布里托马特'鱼叉加农炮

Description: 伊利里亚是一款过时的型号, 但是它也能把你带到你想去的地方.
Name: 李德彼特&斯坦罗德公司 '伊利里亚'

Description: "用这个这就对了." 一个足够对付小型海兽和菜鸟海盗的武器.
Name: 李德彼特&斯坦罗德公司 修复型护卫舰甲板炮 II型

Description: 尾巴上的毒刺.
Name: 李德彼特&斯坦罗德公司 '天蝎座'

Description: '蛀船虫' 鱼雷发射器轻便而致命.不要小瞧它们.
Name: 李德彼特&斯坦罗德公司 '蛀船虫'

Description: "把綠色的死水攪個天翻地覆!" 允许进行鱼雷攻击.
Name: 李德彼特&斯坦罗德公司 '风车'

ChangeDescriptionText: 10|Apparently you've agreed to find the mother of Maybe's Daughter~1000|You've found her mother!~2000|She wants to visit Penstock, in  London~3000|You discouraged her from passing through the Wicket~4000|She passed through the Wicket, and is gone~5000|She passed through the Wicket, and has achieved an understanding with the Bazaar~20|You're searching for the mother of Maybe's Daughter. Your chances will improve with every port you search: Whither, the Isle of Cats, Irem, the Chelonate, Khan's Shadow, Port Carnelian or the Surface port of Naples
Description: 你能多相信她?
LevelDescriptionText: 10|Find her mother in one of these places: Whither, the Isle of Cats, Irem, the Chelonate, Khan's Shadow, Port Carnelian or the Surface port of Naples~1000|Found her mother~2000|Visit Penstock, in London~3000|You discouraged her from passing through the Wicket~4000|She passed through the Wicket, and is gone~5000|She passed through the Wicket, and has achieved an understanding with the Bazaar
Name: 了解事实:某位的女儿

ChangeDescriptionText: 2|The Bandaged Poissonnier requires Strange Catches and Live Specimens for his culinary research.~4|The Bandaged Poissonnier wants to study butchery at the Chelonate.~5|The Bandaged Poissonnier requires zzoup and mutersalt.~6|The Bandaged Poissonnier has mysterious business in Khan's Heart.~7|The Bandaged Poissonnier requires either a Colossal Fluke-Core or an Elegiac Cockatoo.~8|The Bandaged Poissonnier is ready to prepare a feast at the Fathomking's Hold.~10|The Bandaged Poissonnier created a feast for the Fathomking.~3|The Bandaged Poissonnier requires more Strange Catches or Live Specimens for his culinary research.~1|A Bandaged Poissonnier at Venderbight seeks passage with a zee-captain sympathetic to intrepid cuisine.
Description: 谁把他吸引到了海上?

Name: 了解事实: 缠绷带的海鲜厨师

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You've cracked the Brisk Campaigner's reserve.~2|You've seen the Brisk Campaigner collapse.~3|You've elected to help the Brisk Campaigner find what she needs.~50|The Brisk Campaigner has recovered!~100|You won't see the Campaigner again.~90|The Campaigner ended your affair.~101|The Campaigner has become your viceroy.
Description: 她的沉默中有一道轻微的裂痕.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|You've cracked the Brisk Campaigner's reserve~2|You've seen the Brisk Campaigner collapse~3|You've elected to help the Brisk Campaigner find what she needs~50|The Brisk Campaigner has recovered~100|You won't see the Campaigner again~90|The Campaigner ended your affair.~101|The Campaigner has become your viceroy.
Name: 了解事实: 敏锐的军医

ChangeDescriptionText: 5|You dined with the Exile.~10|You made a choice.~11|You've visited the Exile in her cabin.~20|You answered the Exile's question.
Description: 她会变成什么?
LevelDescriptionText: 20|You answered the Exile's question.~5|You dined with the Exile.~10|You made a choice.~11|You've visited the Exile in her cabin.
Name: 了解事实: 玛瑙港的放逐者

ChangeDescriptionText: 115|The Cladery Heart zails south.~120|The Heir looks resolute.~121|The matter is concluded.
Description: 你们日益熟络, 这安全吗?
LevelDescriptionText: 60|Seeking knowledge of the Cladery Heart in Adam's Way~70|Gaining knowledge of the Cladery Heart in Adam's Way~80|Learning how to retrieve the Cladery Heart~90|Seeking the Cladery Heart in Khan's Shadow~20|Aware of the Cladery Heir's claims of parentage~30|Informed of the Cladery Heir's (possible) relationship to Mr Iron~100|Still seeking the Cladery Heart in Khan's Shadow~110|Looking for the Cladery Heart in Frostfound~40|Gathering details on the history of the Cladery Heir~120|Determining the future of the Cladery Heart~121|Finished choosing the fate of the Cladery Heart~115|Retriever of the Cladery Heart, which awaits in Port Carnelian~10|Alerted to rumours about the Cladery Heir's parentage
Name: 了解事实: 覆叶的继承人

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You have dined with the Haunted Doctor.~3|You have wined the Haunted Doctor.~5|The Haunted Doctor has unburdened himself.~6|The Haunted Doctor is different...~100|The Doctor is gone.~101|The Doctor has become your viceroy.
Description: 你对什么东西困扰着他有个模糊的了解.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|You have dined with the Haunted Doctor~5|The Haunted Doctor has unburdened himself~3|You have wined the Haunted Doctor~6|The Doctor is different...~100|The Doctor is gone~101|The Doctor has become your viceroy.
Name: 了解事实: 被困扰的医生

ChangeDescriptionText: 10|Travel to Demeaux Island~200|The Cannoneer has completed his masterwork~100|Take the Seal, and a Judgements' Egg, to the Iron Republic~150|Take the Seal to the heartmetal smith at Station III~50|Travel to Aestival, in the East~500|You have sacrificed the Cannoneer to Zaira
Description: 那个炮手有冷静的一面; 尽管不是太冷静.
LevelDescriptionText: 200|The Cannoneer has completed his masterwork~100|Take the Seal, and a Judgements' Egg, to the Iron Republic~150|Take the Seal to the heartmetal smith at Station III~10|Travel to Demeaux Island~50|Travel to Aestival, in the East~500|The Cannoneer is locked in the Rose Garden
Name: 了解事实: 桀骜不驯的炮手

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|The Magician's story continues.~100|He's gone.~101|The Magician has become your viceroy.
Description: 你现在知道了一点点他的过去.
LevelDescriptionText: 101|The Magician has become your viceroy.
Name: 了解事实: 魔术师

Description: 盛装杀手.
LevelDescriptionText: 20|You have dined with the Modiste~30|The Modiste has made herself at home~50|The Modiste seeks a new challenge in Polythreme~70|You have recovered a strange ushabti~60|The Modiste hunts an old friend~199|You have made an enemy of the Modiste~999|The Modiste is no more~80|The Modiste has reunited with an old friend~100|The Modiste has completed her work~55|The Modiste is on a Mission~200|The Modiste has struck once more~150|The Modiste is keeping to herself~0|The Modiste is a mystery
Name: 了解事实: 无情的衣帽商

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You are learning about the Nacreous Outcast.
Description: 我閃耀 / 至墜落
LevelDescriptionText: 1|You are learning about the Nacreous Outcast
Name: 了解事实: 珍珠流放者

ChangeDescriptionText: 15|You've abandoned the Presbyterate Adventuress to assassins~20|You've helped the Presbyterate Adventuress survive an attack by her assassins~50|You've thrown the Adventuress off your ship~100|The Adventuress has asked you to help her die properly~200|You've been asked to bring 5 units of Romantic Literature, probably from the Khanate, to Abbey Rock~300|Tomorrow she'll fight the Sisters' Adversary at Abbey Rock~400|She's sought comfort with the Campaigner, and tomorrow she'll fight the Sisters' Adversary at Abbey Rock~500|She's ready to fight the Sisters' Adversary at Abbey Rock~1000|She died in combat against the Sisters' Adversary~2000|You watched her die in combat against the Sisters' Adversary
Description: 你了解了一点是什么驱使着她.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|An Acquaintance~10|A Close Acquaintance~15|Abandoned to Assassins~50|Abandoned to her Fate~20|Fought in her Defence~100|Help her Die Well~200|Bring 5 units of Romantic Literature, probably from the Khanate, to Abbey Rock~400|She's sought comfort with the Campaigner, and tomorrow she'll fight the Sisters' Adversary at Abbey Rock~500|She's ready to fight the Sisters' Adversary at Abbey Rock~300|Tomorrow she'll fight the Sisters' Adversary at Abbey Rock~1000|She died in combat against the Sisters' Adversary~2000|You watched her die in combat against the Sisters' Adversary
Name: 了解事实: 古大陆的女探险家
