Name: 目标: 死亡侨民

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|The Venturer has a request... speak to him further, or check your Journal
Description: 他想要...
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Find seven Strange Catches or seven Hunting Trophies~2|Find seven Hunting Trophies or seven pieces of Scintillack~3|Find seven pieces of Scintillack or seven volumes of Romantic Literature~4|Find seven volumes of Romantic Literature or twenty-one bolts of Spider-Silk~5|Find twenty-one bolts of Spider-Silk, or seven skins of Zzoup~6|Find seven skins of Zzoup, or seven packages of Mutersalt~7|Find seven packages of Mutersalt, or seven Devilbone Dice~8|Find seven Devilbone Dice, or seven Outlandish Artefacts~9|Find seven Outlandish Artefacts, or seven bales of Parabola-Linen~10|Find seven bales of Parabola-Linen, or seven pieces of Stygian Ivory~11|Find seven pieces of Stygian Ivory, or seven Caskets of Sapphires~12|Find seven Caskets of Sapphires, or one Lorn-Fluke Core~13|Find one Lorn-Fluke Core, or seven Lamentable Relics~14|Find seven Lamentable Relics, or seven Sacks of Darkdrop Coffee
Name: 目标: 冒险家的欲望

Description: 你船上的仪器依赖于夜晚的能量. 你也许使用了不明仪器.
Name: Obscure Energies

Description: You are playing with the original Pigmote Isle
Name: OldPigmote

Description: 这个属于博物馆!假定殖民帝国对税务支配权进行拨款是对不同文化间接触的合理反应.也许吧, 因为博物馆是个复杂而庞大的官僚机构.  [如果你订立了遗嘱,你可以把这个转化为一件继承物来留给你的继任者.]
Name: 异国的工艺品

Description: 没有氧气的话, 你的潜艇就仅仅是个金属坟墓.
Name: 氧气

Description: 晦涩但是有时却很实用的知识. [增加你将碎片转化为秘密的速度.]
Name: 书页值

Description: 举起一面镜子看着镜子中的它: 一只豹子的幼崽, 身上长着像午夜雾气一样的灰色绒毛,但是透着琥珀的光泽.
Name: 帕布拉的小猫

Description: 一只威严的琥珀色大猫, 因为其对马鲛鱼的爱好而闻名. 但是水手对待她总是带有一种夸张的尊敬. 他们见过她在镜子中的样子...
Name: 帕布拉豹

Description: 小而敏捷,令人畏惧,就像一只发怒的野鼠.
Name: 普罗赛德级武装快艇

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|A Dilemma! How will you advise Pigmote Isle?~0|You have resolved the dilemma, for better or worse.
Description: 你的建议是?
Name: 皮格莫特岛: 进退两难

Description: 一定要建立一个国家. 如果这达到0, 皮格莫特岛上会发生不好的事情.
LevelDescriptionText: 0|Catastrophe~1|DANGER~7|Cultured~9|Dignified~10|Magnificent~8|Distinguished~2|Danger~5|Unexceptional~6|Rising~3|Struggling~4|Troubled
Name: 皮格莫特岛: 文明之光

ChangeDescriptionText: 40|The battle for Pigmote Isle has begun. Return later to see the outcome.~99|Pigmote Isle has fallen.~1|Hail Cavia!~2|Hail Murinia!~21|Cavia has allied with Visage.~22|Murinia has allied with Visage.~31|Cavia has allied with the Fathomking.~32|Murinia has allied with the Fathomking.~51|Hail United Cavia!~52|Hail United Murinia!~62|Murinia fights for independence.~61|Cavia fights for independence.~95|You have been banished from Pigmote Isle.
Description: 两股势力,相似的权威.请注意言行.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Cavia~2|Murinia~51|United Cavia~52|United Murinia~61|Cavia (Fighting For Independence)~62|Murinia (Fighting For Independence)~21|Cavia and Visage~22|Murinia and Visage~32|Murinia and His Complexity~95|You have been banished from Pigmote Isle~99|Pigmote has fallen~31|Cavia and His Complexity
Name: 皮格莫特岛: 统治与征服

Description: 国家一定要强大. 如果这达到0, 皮格莫特岛上会发生不好的事情.
LevelDescriptionText: 7|Strong~9|Mighty~10|Ascendant~0|Catastrophe~8|Hardy~1|DANGER~2|Danger~3|Weak~5|Adequate~6|Unimposing~4|Vulnerable
Name: 皮格莫特岛: 力量

ChangeDescriptionText: 31|Pigmote's fate has been decided.~1|A new nation has been founded.~2|Time passes on Pigmote Isle.~30|Pigmote must decide its fate.~40|Pigmote's war for independence has begun.~999|Life continues on Pigmote Isle.~99|Pigmote lies in ruins.~10|Pigmote Isle approaches a crossroads.~8|Great ships have been dispatched to Pigmote Isle.~6|The eyes of the zee turn to Pigmote Isle.
Description: 地下世界最可爱的帝国中,时间正在流逝.
LevelDescriptionText: 31|Pigmote's fate has been decided~1|A new nation has been founded~40|Pigmote fights for independence~999|Life continues on Pigmote Isle~99|Pigmote's dream is over~30|Pigmote must decide its fate
Name: 皮格莫特岛: 建国之路

Description: 国家需要希望. 如果这达到0, 皮格莫特岛上会发生不好的事情.
LevelDescriptionText: 0|Catastrophe~9|Delighted~10|Triumphant~1|DANGER~2|Danger~3|Conflicted~5|Content~4|Argumentative~6|Optimistic~7|Pleased~8|Happy
Name: 皮格莫特岛: 精神

Description: 像人类的心, 但不是很像.毕竟,最后,她只是粘土.
Name: 海盗诗人之心

Description: 他可能不会锯错腿.
Name: 看似可靠的医生

Description: 但是谁是猫,谁是鼠?
LevelDescriptionText: 4|An Absentee Aunt~5|An Eccentric Burglar~6|A Deranged Medium~1|A Disgruntled Naval Officer~2|A Masked Clay Man~3|An Enterprising Astronomer
Name: 和一个正在逃避的目标做猫鼠游戏

Description: 你的船正在享受气动传输带来的好处.
Name: 气动老鼠传输机

AvailableAt: Sometimes available for hire in London.
Description: 也许她害怕被忘记. 但是除此之外她无所畏惧.
Name: 古大陆的女探险家

Description: 这是个未付的报酬.
Name: 未付的报酬

Description: "给我带来海胆的核心,作为我的王."
Name: 珊瑚之源的结局:一个海胆核心

Description: "带给我一小块燧石, 作为我的卒," 珊瑚之源说
Name: 珊瑚之源的结局: 一小块燧石

Description: "给我带来怪物的牙齿, 作为我新的骑士.", 珊瑚之源说
Name: 珊瑚之源的结局: 怪物的牙齿

Description: "带给我一个警觉的雕像, 做我的新主教," 珊瑚之源说
Name: 珊瑚之源的结局: 一个警觉的雕像

Description: "心壳银, 作为我的新堡垒", 珊瑚之源说.
Name: 珊瑚之源的结局: 心壳银

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Opening moves.~2|Initial gambits.~3|Developments.~4|Gambits answered.~5|An extra move.~6|An opening.~10|A minor piece.~25|At the end-game~100|A stalemate~200|A victory
Description: 珊瑚正在变化...
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Pursuing chess in the Principles~5|Speaking with the Principles~10|Seeking the Salt-Lions~15|Seeking further pieces~25|At the end-game~200|A victory~100|A stalemate~11|Returning with Sphinxstone
Name: 珊瑚之源的结局: 珊瑚国度

Description: 你在珊瑚之源的象棋比赛中有了自己的记号.
Name: 珊瑚之源的结局:有原则的比赛

Description: 你把这个倒霉的家伙关在了货仓底的笼子里. [囚犯靠剩饭维生一般情况下不消耗你的补给品. 通过使用这件物品释放你的囚犯, 或者出于某种目的把他们带回伦敦...]
Name: 囚犯

AvailableAt: 囚犯被囚禁在达哈.
Description: 这个前囚犯正向玫瑰之门旅行.
Name: 从溺亡者处解救的囚犯

Description: 你在一艘灯塔船上放了真菌虫.
Name: 播种: 灯塔船

Description: 你在修道院岩礁放了真菌虫. 毫无疑问如果修女们反对,她们会做出一些反应.
Name: 播种:修道院岩礁

Description: 你在亚当之路放下了真菌虫.
Name: 播种: 亚当之路

Description: 你在阿斯蒂沃放下了真菌虫, 看起来真丢人.
Name: 播种: 阿斯蒂沃

AvailableAt: 安忒
Description: 你在安忒放下了真菌虫.
Name: 播种: 安忒

Description: 你仁慈地把真菌虫带向了那么多的岛屿.
Name: 播种: 真菌虫上岸

Description: 你在达哈放下了真菌虫.
Name: 播种: 达哈

Description: 你在德莫岛放下了真菌虫.
Name: 播种: 德莫岛

Description: 你向手掌帝国介绍了真菌虫.
Name: 播种: 手掌帝国

Description: 你在加德的哀悼放下了真菌虫. 也许它们能在某处找到安身之地.
Name: 播种: 加德的哀悼

Description: 你在神落放下了真菌虫.毫无疑问它们能在破碎城堡的走廊里找到养分.
Name: 播种: 神落

Description: 你在隐逸之地放下了真菌虫. 也许他们会和下面的巨兽做朋友.
Name: 播种: 隐逸之地

Description: 你在猎户塔楼放下了真菌虫.
Name: 播种: 猎户塔楼

Description: 你在伊瑞暮放下了真菌虫. 或者, 也许, 你将会散播它们.
Name: 播种: 伊瑞暮

Description: 你在可汗之心放下了真菌虫.
Name: 播种: 可汗之心

Description: 你在可汗之影放下了真菌虫.
Name: 播种: 可汗之影

Description: 真菌虫在水下也很开心, 尤其是水可供呼吸的情况下.
Name: 播种: 旮旯

Description: 没什么能在这里扎根.
Name: 播种: 不在噬王者的城堡

Description: 你在农西奥放下了真菌虫.
Name: 播种: 农西奥

Description: 你在皮格莫特放下了真菌虫...也许是在微妙的平衡中引入了第三个势力.
Name: 播种:皮格莫特岛

Description: 你在碎心国放下了真菌虫.谁知道会发生什么事情?
Name: 播种: 碎心国

Description: 你在玛瑙港放下了真菌虫.
Name: 播种: 玛瑙港

Description: 你在玫瑰之门放下了真菌虫. 希望他们不介意烟味.
Name: 播种: 玫瑰之门

Description: 你在救世主岩礁放下了真菌虫.他们会填满所有没被蜘蛛网堵住的黑暗缝隙.
Name: 播种: 救世主岩礁

Description: 你在骨雕馆放下了真菌虫.
Name: 播种: 骨雕馆

Description: 你在牧羊人岛放下了真菌虫. 没人会相信的.
Name: 播种: 牧羊人岛

Description: 真菌虫悄悄潜入了加了三道锁的大门里.
Name: 播种: 要塞 III

Description: 你在光之礼拜堂放下了真菌虫.他们不会很享受这些东西的.
Name: 播种: 光之礼拜堂

Description: 你在切洛内特放下了真菌虫.
Name: 播种: 切洛内特

Description: 显然真菌虫在城堡里很受欢迎.
Name: 播种: 深寻王的城堡

Description: 真菌虫在死者之间会过得很好的.
Name: 播种: 刚特极点

Description: 真菌虫在这里. 曾经在这里.或至少将要在这里.
Name: 播种: 钢铁共和国

Description: 你在猫岛放下了真菌虫. 这会对蜜蜂有什么影响?
Name: 播种: 猫岛

Description: 真菌虫们会在红树林深处茁壮成长.
Name: 播种: 红树学院

Description: 在这些石头巨兽的缝隙里, 真菌虫开始成长.
Name: 播种: 盐狮

Description: 你将真菌虫放到了爪下.
Name: 播种: 爪下

Description: 也许你的真菌虫会在米希尔的光照下行走.
Name: 播种: 瓦尔查斯

Description: 你为死亡聚居地带来了些新的, 紫色的生命.
Name: 播种: 文登湾

Description: 你在维瑟吉放下了真菌虫. 它很难让这个地方变得更陌生.
Name: 播种: 维瑟吉

Description: 你在船墟放下了真菌虫.
Name: 播种: 船墟

Description: "你需要一些人去查看里面." [法布尔鼠助手对于气动老鼠传输机来说必不可少.]
Name: 法布尔鼠助手

Description: 发出炽热的星海黄色光. 它吸收着不属于这个世界的辐射. 它的一些颜色只能在梦中看到.
Name: Ray-Drenched Cinder

Description: 远方的殖民地通常很渴望这些消息. [你同时最多持有一份最新资讯.]
Name: 最新资讯

Description: 你已经经历过甜蜜而无梦的一夜. [这将会在你对抗梦魇时增强你的力量.]
Name: 安静的一晚

Description: 啊呀! [黑墨镜将军会想要看到这个, 如果海军对你的好感足够高.]
Name: 秘密海图

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You have a child~10|You are a father~11|You are a mother~12|You are something significant in this child's life. They call you 'Captain'~20|Your child has gone to zee!
Description: 出生或者领养, 他们是你的.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|You have a child~10|Your child calls you Father~11|Your child calls you Mother~12|Your child calls you Captain~20|Your child has gone to zee
Name: 浪漫: 一个伦敦的孩子

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Something new.
Description: 发生了一些事情.
Name: 浪漫: 显眼的场合

ChangeDescriptionText: 2|You have begun an affair with the Longshanks Gunner~1|You have begun an affair with the Sly Navigator~3|You have begun an affair with the Tireless Mechanic~4|You have begun an affair with the Campaigner~5|You have begun an affair with the Nacreous Survivor~6|You have begun an affair with the Magician~7|You have begun an affair with Maybe's Daughter~8|You have begun an affair with the Cladery Heir
Description: 心是无心的猎人. [你和一名船官开始了一段谨慎的关系.]
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Sly Navigator~2|Longshanks Gunner~8|Cladery Heir~4|Campaigner~3|Mechanic~7|The Daughter~6|Magician~5|Nacreous Survivor
Name: 浪漫: 和...的关系

ChangeDescriptionText: 0|For now, your affair with your officer is forgotten.~1|You have fraternised with one of your officers.
Description: 你和一名船官开始了一段关系, 在海泽之上.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|You have been fraternising with one of your officers.
Name: 浪漫: 黑暗中的爱情

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You have a sweetheart in London.~0|They're gone.~100|You had a sweetheart in London
Description: 你选择了伦敦的爱人.
Name: 浪漫: 有些人回家了

Description: 所有心的历险都在这里, 用散文,诗歌或者绘画. 有些也许更适合私人享用. [附注:在伦敦, 所有的爱情故事都要缴税.即使是虚构的爱情故事也一样.]
Name: 爱情小说

ChangeDescriptionText: 10|Cultivating a bitter flavour: the taste of sharp chocolate.~1|Cultivating a bitter flavour: the taste of mild coffee.~20|Cultivating a bitter flavour: the taste of burnt rope.~30|Cultivating a bitter flavour: the taste of winter wind.~40|Cultivating a bitter flavour: the taste of hot pitch.~50|Cultivating a bitter flavour: the taste of brimstone.
Description: 用来点燃心智.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Mild coffee~10|Sharp chocolate~20|Burnt rope~30|Winter wind~40|Hot pitch~50|Brimstone
Name: 玫瑰之门: 苦口之味

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You have agreed to transport the Dogged Apprentice to the Grand Geode.
Description: 他的主人远行至此寻找烟草.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|A dejected youth, headed for the Grand Geode~2|A recovering youth, headed for the Grand Geode
Name: 玫瑰之门: 顽固的学徒

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You have agreed to take the Dogged Apprentice to Rosegate.~10|The Crotchety Tobacconist would like you to aid in the creation of his underwater cigar.~15|The cigar is nearly complete.~20|You dashed the hopes of the Crotchety Tobacconist ever creating his underwater cigar.~45|You have agreed to deliver the Crotchety Tobacconist to the Iron Republic.~50|You have dropped off the Crotchety Tobacconist, to begin mass production of his underwater cigars.~25|You have agreed to deliver the Crotchety Tobacconist to the Iron Republic.~40|You aided the Crotchety Tobacconist in creating the underwater cigar.	~30|The Crotchety Tobacconist will wallow within the Iron Republic.
Description: 每人都有个梦.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|You are delivering the Dogged Apprentice and his rumbling crate to Rosegate~15|The cigar is nearly complete~10|You are assisting in the realisation of an underwater cigar~25|You are delivering the Crotchety Tobacconist to the Iron Republic~45|You are delivering the Crotchety Tobacconist to the Iron Republic~50|The Crotchety Tobacconist will mass produce his underwater cigar in the Iron Republic~30|The Crotchety Tobacconist will wallow within the Iron Republic~20|You dashed the hopes of the Crotchety Tobacconist ever creating his underwater cigar~40|You aided the Crotchety Tobacconist in creating the underwater cigar
Name: 玫瑰之门: 烟草的命运

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|The Dogged Apprentice has been harvested.~2|You have been harvested.~3|The cigar has been destroyed.
Description: 如果不包装怎么能叫雪茄.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|A taste of hate~2|A taste of passion~3|Obliteration
Name: 玫瑰之门: 最后的味道

ChangeDescriptionText: 10|Cultivating a luscious flavour: the taste of an apple slice.~30|Cultivating a luscious flavour: the taste of a Surface rose.~40|Cultivating a luscious flavour: the taste of a Viennese greenhouse.~50|Cultivating a luscious flavour: the taste of a beloved's perfume.~20|Cultivating a luscious flavour: the taste of a fresh-baked pie.~1|Cultivating a luscious flavour: the taste of a stale pastry.
Description: 燃烧.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|A stale pastry~10|An apple slice~30|A Surface rose~40|A Viennese greenhouse~50|A beloved's perfume~20|A fresh-baked pie
Name: 玫瑰之门: 甘美之味

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Cultivating a robust flavour: the taste of kettle steam.~10|Cultivating a robust flavour: the taste of watery beer.~20|Cultivating a robust flavour: the taste of marrow broth.~30|Cultivating a robust flavour: the taste of well-aged wine.~40|Cultivating a robust flavour: the taste of warm blood.~50|Cultivating a robust flavour: the taste of fecund earth.
Description: 支撑.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Kettle steam~10|Watery beer~20|Marrow broth~30|Well-aged wine~40|Warm blood~50|Fecund earth
Name: 玫瑰之门: 强健之味

Description: 每分每秒, 每日每周, 每月, 每年 对他而言都是痛苦.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|He won't wait forever~16|He can wait no longer
Name: 玫瑰之门: 烟草匠减退的耐心

AvailableAt: 狩猎蓝色先知或者衣帽商蝙蝠来获取这个.
Description: 发出思想的光,像珠宝一样的光
Name: 宝蓝色羽毛

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Bound for both the Cumaean Canal and the Iron and Misery Co. Funging Station.~5|Ready to visit the chess tournament in Port Cecil.~10|The immortal man is dead!~100|You have refused to carry him farther.~15|Bound for Kingeater's Castle.~20|A promise of liberty, equality, and eternity.~50|He's on his own.~3|You were to visit the Cumaean Canal and the Iron and Misery Co. Funging Station; there is still one port left to visit.
Description: 好说格言的寻乐者有个任务. "上面会永远改变," 他说.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Bound for both the Cumaean Canal and the Iron and Misery Co. Funging Station~5|Ready to visit the chess tournament in Port Cecil~10|The immortal man is dead!	~100|You refused to carry the Gnomic Gallivant any farther after he set off a bomb at the chess tournament~20|The Gnomic Gallivant spoke to an invisible master. You have been promised liberty, equality, and eternity~15|Bound for Kingeater's Castle~50|You refused to help the Gnomic Gallivant with his plot.~3|You were to visit the Cumaean Canal and the Iron and Misery Co. Funging Station; there is still one port left to visit
Name: 红宝石色的写作

Description: 加德的哀悼那边的海盗告诉了你许多关于那个粘土海匪的故事.
LevelDescriptionText: 0|The Pirate-Poet is roaming the zee~5|The Pirate-Poet is being hunted~6|The Pirate-Poet is not currently at zee~99|The Pirate-Poet is believed dead~90|The Pirate-Poet is said to be lost at zee~10|The Pirate-Poet is believed to be a prisoner
Name: 关于海盗诗人的流言

Description: 所有的地狱之火, 还有所有的天堂之馨.
Name: 一包暗涌咖啡豆

Description: 在没东西可供拿取之前, 你能提供多少?
Name: 麻袋和雪: 刺骨寒冷的存在

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|The Snow Child is starting to thaw.~2|The Snow Child is beginning to melt.~3|The Snow Child is struggling.~4|The Snow Child fights to stay together.~40|The Snow Child will no longer melt.
Description: 融化是它的本质.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|The Snow Child is well-frozen by the chill of the North~2|The Snow Child has begun to thaw~3|The Snow Child leaves puddles where it walks~4|The Snow Child has little time left~40|The Snow Child is stable~99|The Snow Child has melted
Name: 麻袋和雪: 雪之心

ChangeDescriptionText: 20|You are in the Service of Mr Sacks.~10|You turned away Mr Sacks. Nothing bad can possibly come of this.~30|You have been given your first delivery.~39|You have completed your first delivery.~40|You have been given your second delivery.~49|You have completed your second delivery.~50|You have been given your third delivery.~70|Your service is concluded.~99|You bought your way out of Service.
Description: 花了太长时间, 他可能会带上你.
LevelDescriptionText: 20|Mr Sacks has taken your Service~10|You turned away Mr Sacks~39|You have made your first delivery for Mr Sacks~49|You have made your second delivery for Mr Sacks~50|Mr Sacks requires passage to the Avid Horizon~70|Something awaits you in your Lodgings~80|Your service to Mr Sacks is concluded~99|You bought your way out of Service~40|You must deliver a jewelled bird to the Isle of Cats or Mutton Island~30|You must deliver hunger to Khan's Heart or Pigmote Isle
Name: 麻袋和雪: 为麻袋先生服务

ChangeDescriptionText: 2|You have named the Snow Child
LevelDescriptionText: 2|Chione~3|Loki~4|Boreas~5|Winter~6|Snegurochka~7|Elliot~8|Rose~1|Snow Child
Name: 麻袋和雪: 雪孩子的名字

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You have created a snow child.~2|You spoke to the Snow Child.~7|The Snow Child has made a wish.~10|You know how to help the Snow Child.~20|The Snow Child is complete.~99|The Snow Child is no more.~5|The Snow Child has joined the ship.~80|The Snow Child's real story has begun.~88|You abandoned the Snow Child.
Description: 雪孩子生于渴求之地平线.
LevelDescriptionText: 5|You have named the Snow Child~2|You have spoken to the Snow Child~20|The Snow Child will head East from Irem~1|You have helped create a snow child~7|The Snow Child wants to go East - if you can stop it melting~10|You have learned that the Snow Child requires Heartmetal~80|The Snow Child has begun its journey~88|The Snow Child returned home~99|The Snow Child melted
Name: 麻袋和雪: 雪会变成什么

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You are recovering salvage.~0|Salvage complete!
Name: 打捞沉船

Description: 它只能持续这么长时间...
LevelDescriptionText: 1|The Festival of Silk begins~6|The Festival of Silk draws to a close~2|The Festival of Silk warms up~3|The Festival of Silk fills the island with cheer~4|The Festival of Silk is in full swing~5|The Festival of Silk feels like it will never end~7|The Festival of Silk is ending~8|The Festival of Silk is over
Name: 救世主岩礁: 在丝物盛会上

Description: 如果你足够幸运,它只会杀了你.
Name: 救世主岩礁: 贪婪的锚爪海胆的愿望

Description: 你遭遇了救世主岩礁的大蜘蛛议会.
LevelDescriptionText: 0|A Stranger to Spiders~99|A Scourge of Spiders~30|A Supplicant of Spiders~90|A Spurner of Spiders~40|A Scavenger for Spiders~50|A Salvager for Spiders~75|A Stooge of Spiders~20|A Supplier to Spiders~10|A Supplier of Tomb Colonists to Spiders?
Name: 救世主岩礁: 被救世主岩礁的蛛网困住

Description: 她还没为这样的一场战斗做好准备!
Name: 救世主岩礁: 完整的夜曲号

Description: 它们一直在看着. 你也是.
Name: 救世主岩礁: 刺探悲伤蜘蛛

Description: 每艘船都有自己的秘密.
Name: 救世主岩礁: 夜曲号的命运

Description: 救世主岩礁正在感谢那些慷慨的邻居
LevelDescriptionText: 1|The Festival of Silk has begun~2|The Festival of Silk is over~5|The Festival of Silk is cancelled~6|The Festival of Silk is cancelled forever
Name: 救世主岩礁: 丝物盛会

Description: 她正在瓦解, 但是至少她离终点不远了.
Name: 救世主岩礁: 夜曲号的最后一次航行

Description: 绝对不是悲伤蜘蛛的卵.把它们送到伦敦去.
Name: 救世主岩礁: 小玩意. 只是些小玩意.

Description: 和救世主岩礁的蜘蛛议会一起等待听众.
Name: 救世主岩礁: 进我的会客厅, 说...

Description: 发出月光一样微光的珊瑚.它可以成为非常棒的珠宝或者极其昂贵的茶.
Name: 闪晶

Description: 你的航行将会继续. [你建立了一个船长的朝代. 这将会在船长之间流传, 除非有些事情发生并终止了它.]
LevelDescriptionText: 1|You have a Scion
Name: 继承者

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|The Lost Pilgrim settles into her bunk with vague contentment as she sails for the Gant Pole
Description: 她有要去骨雕馆的理由. 她也有个理由要去刚特极点. 她几乎已经下定了决心.
Name: 骨雕馆: 迷失的朝圣之旅

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|The Monastic Drownie silently boards your ship, due for Scrimshander
Description: 为骨雕馆而生的沉默溺亡者, 要将生命献给研究.
Name: 骨雕馆: 修道的溺亡者

ChangeDescriptionText: 40|You've left a part of yourself behind for the ivory tower at Scrimshander~25|You have delivered a traveller from Scrimshander~45|You have delivered a traveller from Scrimshander~20|You've learned enough about history to distrust any one person's interpretation~10|You have been to Scrimshander, the City of Remembrance~60|Some questions will remain forever unanswered by history
Description: 不要说得好像这里只有一段历史那样.
LevelDescriptionText: 40|You've left a part of yourself behind for the ivory citadel at Scrimshander.	~20|You've learned enough about history to distrust any one person's interpretation.~10|You have been to Scrimshander, the City of Remembrance.~25|You have delivered a traveller from Scrimshander.~45|You have delivered a traveller from Scrimshander.~60|You have uncovered all of the secrets Scrimshander is willing to offer you.
Name: 骨雕馆: 全史学者

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|The Scholar of Lost Causes grumbles as he settles into his bunk, ready for the trip to Hideaway
Description: 他见人们战斗过, 见人们为自己的目标献身. 现在, 他正在找一名隐逸之地的幸存者.
Name: 骨雕馆: 消逝史学者

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|The Truth-Hunting Chelonate boards your ship, where she eagerly scans the waves for Scrimshander
Description: 一名年老的猎人来到了骨雕馆, 寻找她祖先的伟大故事.
Name: 骨雕馆: 狩猎真理的切洛内特人

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You have delivered the Cargo of Answers to the Drownies.~2|You have delivered the Cargo of Answers to the Chelonates.~3|You are to deliver the Cargo to the Fathomking.~4|You must return to Scrimshander to report the Fathomking's Judgement.~5|You must return to Scrimshander to report the Fathomking's Judgement.~6|You have settled the history of the Chelonate.~7|You are to accompany a Monk into the Archives in Scrimshander.~10|You have settled the history of the Chelonate.~8|You must return to the Chelonate Chronologist in Scrimshander.~9|You must return to the Chelonate Chronologist in Scrimshander.
Description: 你从残骸中找回了一箱骨雕. 那货物本来是要送去骨雕馆的.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|You gave the Cargo of Answers to the Drownies~2|You gave the Cargo of Answers to the Chelonates~3|You have accepted a task to go to the Fathomking~5|You counselled the Fathomking to strike the Chelonate from his songs~6|You have settled the history of the Cargo of Answers~7|You are to accompany a monk to the archives~8|You sealed the monk, and the Cargo of Answers, into a forgotten vault~9|You uncovered an alternate history of the Chelonate~10|You have settled the history of the Cargo of Answers~4|You counselled the Fathomking to make public the Chelonate's shameful history
Name: 骨雕馆: 递送答案货物

Description: 切洛内特的猎人们相信历史是英雄故事的结局. 一名明智的史学家从他们的行动中得到了启示并皈依了他们的英雄行为.
Name: 骨雕馆: 关于英雄的历史

ChangeDescriptionText: 10|You seek ancient knowledge in the Ivory Archives~20|The Drownie Chorus will pay handsomely for what you've uncovered
Description: 英雄来来去去, 但是他们的故事被混乱的年代淹没, 被潮水冲刷. 骨雕大厅的溺亡者会向你支付大量报酬来换取幽暗储藏库中特别的故事.
LevelDescriptionText: 10|Search the Ivory Archives for historical patterns~20|Share the patterns of history you've found with the Drownie Chorus in Scrimshander's amphitheatre
Name: 骨雕馆: 幽暗储藏库: 变化的环境

Description: 据说幽暗储藏库中有些东西能追溯到历史的开端. 但是没人知道那到底是什么.
Name: 骨雕馆: 幽暗储藏库: 探寻过去

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You remember fine tea and conversation in the depths of the Ivory Archives~2|You've uncovered the deepest history of Scrimshander
Description: 在幽暗储藏库里找到有意思的东西了, 不是吗?
LevelDescriptionText: 1|You've found who lives in the depths of the archives.~2|You've found Scrimshander's first skeleton, and the history of the tower itself.
Name: 骨雕馆: 幽暗储藏库: 历史的启示

ChangeDescriptionText: 10|You seek a hero's tale in the Ivory Archives~20|The Chelonate's champions will pay handsomely for what you've discovered.
Description: 切洛内特的大战士想要演一出关于伟大英雄的戏剧. 在档案馆中找到材料, 然后他们会给你一个英雄的奖励. 不是暗讽他们戏剧中的那些故事.
LevelDescriptionText: 10|Uncover the tale of a great hero in the Ivory Archives~20|Share the heroic tale with the Chelonate's champions in Scrimshander's amphitheatre.
Name: 骨雕馆: 幽暗储藏库: 寻找医生

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You've added a finger to the bones of Scrimshander~4|You've added a handful of fingers to the bones of Scrimshander
Description: 一根或多根你的指骨都能从骨雕馆白骨墙上换取故事. 至于你的手...没什么是一双填了料的手套掩饰不了的.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|You have sacrificed one of your fingers to Scrimshander.~2|Some of your fingers now decorate the city of Scrimshander.~4|You've given Scrimshander a handful of your fingers.
Name: 骨雕馆: 失去的手指

Description: 溺亡者学者相信历史是个永不停歇的回环. 明智的学者可以从每个时代的潮水中得到启示.
Name: 骨雕馆: 时间之潮

Description: 幽暗储藏库被小心翼翼地保护着. 就像大多数在档案馆中的人一样, 任何逗留时间超过受欢迎程度的人都有可能惨遭不幸.
Name: 骨雕馆: 档案馆中的时间

Description: 骨雕记录者的心已经很疲惫, 但是他的食物十分丰盛... 他几乎会用一切东西煲汤.
Name: Scrimshaw Chronicler

Description: 一块从天而降伤痕累累的陨铁, 有一辆独轮车那么大.它的两侧有发光的符文.
Name: 红科技的封印

Description: 秘密就是火焰. 真理会燃烧.
Name: 炽热的谜团

Description: 所有好事的根源. [和你的船官讨论秘密来提升技能. 你可以通过右键点击他们的头像来和他们交谈.]
Name: Secret

Description: 确保没人能在没有钥匙的情况下进去...或者出来.[这能防止你的货物被贪婪的乘客偷走,或者让你安全的运输一些活东西.]
Name: 安全货柜

Description: 看着它如何在水中滑行. 就像月光一样.
Name: 平静的水族箱

Description: 他能让这些补给可以入口, 尽管不是很美味.
Name: 阴暗的厨师

Description: 某种荣誉.
Name: 闪耀的骑士

Description: 一个雕刻着南方的印记的神龛,闪闪发光.
Name: 石神的神龛

Description: 和人类相比他更像是纯粹的符文.但是他能把你带向正确的方向.
Name: 吞噬符文的领航员

AvailableAt: 有时候可以在伦敦雇用, 或者去羊岛找他.
Description: 那个纹身在你上次看到他之后又变大了?
Name: 浑身符文的领航员

Description: 胜任? 也许. 可靠? 没准.
Name: 狡猾的领航员

Description: 一件古怪的心金属武器.
Name: 铁匠的苦恼

Description: 不可思议的新技术能带你穿越冥河! 不要熄灭它.  [一件能胜任搜寻敌人任务的设备.]
Name: 柔和的灯晶灯

AvailableAt: 这个会生长在红树学院附近的幽深小路中.
Description: 只要一两个,就能让你开心与振奋.但是吃得太多有可能让你体验到世间最美妙的死法.
Name: 慰藉之果

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|The waves are flecked with light.~50|Zee-bats cry out. They are nothing like birds.~39|Something drifts, face-down.~47|A false-star flares in the cavern roof directly above you; flares, and fades.~78|A tiny breeze stirs your hair, and dies.~81|Waves slap the side of the ship. Far below, something moves.~40|Some sort of beetle has invaded your morsel of ship's biscuit. It waggles its antennae impertinently.~20|Green glass and basalt. Salt and silence.~37|The glim-lamp at the prow fizzes, arcs.~30|On the horizon, a sickly yellow light glimmers for a moment, then fades.~49|Where is everyone? Where did they go? ...they're here. They're here. You're not alone.~60|Distant bells.~100|Blue lightnings crawl leisurely up the funnel. "St Erasmus dancing!" the cry goes up.~82|Home. Warmly lit windows, company, peace. Thoughts of home come at the strangest times.~90|The air trembles. A breath of change passes...~25|The glassy chop of dark water. The iron clatter of feet at the hatchway.~10|The air carries the scent of salt and shadows.~43|A zailor raises her head, sniffs sharply. Blood on the wind. ~19|The scent of the zee! Salt and frost and cellars. Black spices.~70|Luminescent beasts like eyeless dolphins play in your wake.~68|A zailor is praying.~74|A sluggish wave. The ship pitches.~84|Far off, very far off, someone screams...~86|Laughter from the fore-deck.~88|A belch of smoke goes up from the funnel.~11|The air trembles. A breath of change passes...~12|A belch of smoke goes up from the funnel.~13|Laughter from the fore-deck.~14|Far off, very far off, someone screams...~85|Zee-bats cry out. They are nothing like birds.~16|A zailor is praying.~17|Luminescent beasts like eyeless dolphins play in your wake.~18|A row of watchful zee-bats perch on the ship's railing. Their heads swivel in unison as you cross the deck.~0|That's all for now.~72|A row of watchful zee-bats hang from a cable. Their heads swivel in unison as you cross the deck.~9|A rock breaks the water like a surfacing zee-beast. No, it's a  zee-beast! No, it's a rock.~3|On the Surface, the sun still warms the Earth. Or so one assumes.~5|A brisk spatter of spray. The Unterzee is restless.~7|An electric shiver to the air. Storm is watching, the zailors would say.~22|The waves are cluttered with zee-wrack, like drowned hair drifting.~51|You are being watched.~52|A soft wind from the East. The impossible scent of pine.~53|Waves slap the side of the ship. Far below, something moves.~54|A ship's horn, far away.~55|Blue lightnings crawl leisurely up the funnel. "St Erasmus dancing!" the cry goes up.~150|You are not welcome here. ~101|Something brushes briefly against the shell. The zub shakes.~110|The brightest light cannot reach this depth. That glow is an illusion. ~120|The air is stale. An off-duty crewman keens softly. ~130|Lights glance past the windows. Another zubmarine?  ~140|The Observation Dome is silent. Your navigator's breath is loud in the stillness.~160|A dull tolling echoes around the bridge. A distress bell, now fading.  ~170|A shoal of fish pass by a porthole. The prow-lamp reveals the midnight iridescence of their scales. ~200|The compass shifts in the binnacle. Briefly, you are off-course. The coral is a useless signpost.~190| A diving-suit floats past the glass.~180|The temperature changes abruptly. Your helmsman complains about goosebumps.
Description: 你下次停泊时会找到些新的故事. [当你在海上航行足够的时间后会得到这个.]
LevelDescriptionText: 0|Nothing awaits you. Time to leave port?~1|Stories await when you next make port.
Name: Something Awaits You

Description: 第一眼看上去,它就像是死亡侨民的棺材. 经过仔细检查, 它上面的铭牌上写着苏瑟 & 库珀 还有如下的标签: '遞送到 倉庫 (A), 要塞 III'.
Name: 苏瑟&库珀 长箱

Description: 不确定性调谐: 相比于技术,更多的只是理论. [调谐器不影响你隐匿的能力.]
Name: 不确定性调谐器

Description: 那些破坏者已经把这些破碎而伤心的石材从盐狮的两翼撬了下来.一名伦敦的联络员会交易这些.
Name: 斯芬克斯石

Description: "無法逃避的結局!" 一件发射鱼叉的强力武器.
Name: 斯坦霍德 '圣十字' 鱼叉发射器

Description: 司命是从这冰冷的残骸中孵化出来的吗?或者这完全是另一种东西.不要太凑近看这些伤眼的遗失颜色.
Name: 星壳

AvailableAt: 进行长箱交易可能会让你认识更多的人.
Description: 你为朴素的助手做的工作向你介绍了三号要塞里的其他人.
Name: 要塞 III: 结识心金属铁匠

Description: 你结识了朴素的助手.
Name: 要塞 III: 赢得助手的好感

Description: 一块银色金属锭, 摸起来极其寒冷.
Name: 要塞 III: 心金属锭

Description: 参与到特定的交易中.
Name: 要塞 III: 交易长箱

Description: 实用主义考古学家的工具.
Name: 炸药

Description: 它有可能是某种鱼,但是最好不要离太近看.
Name: 奇怪的猎获

Description: 我的天. 将军绝对很想知道这个.
Name: 战略情报

Description: 这些黑色的海怪骨头可以制作出令人惊讶的束胸衣.
Name: 阴暗黑骨

Description: 也许你想用餐桌大小的小船在海泽中航行是有原因的.
Name: 斯提姆法洛斯级小汽艇

Description: 它非常危险, 但是既然它如此美丽,又有谁在乎呢?
Name: 充满阳光的捕光镜匣

Description: 食物和工具. [如果你耗尽了补给, 饥饿最终会毁掉你.]
Name: 补给

Description: 透镜, 药酒, 蜡烛, 火油.偶尔, 需要骨头.
Name: 工作补给

Description: 确保发动机不会在开足马力时爆炸.
Name: 抑制器

Description: 谁统治着伦敦的第一个地下海殖民地?
LevelDescriptionText: 1|You are working to protect London's interests in Port Carnelian~2|You have furthered the Khan's interests in port Carnelian~3|You are supporting the tigers' aboriginal claim to Port Carnelian~11|You have ensured Port Carnelian will remain squarely under her Majesty's control~12|You engineered the Khanate's annexation of Port Carnelian~13|You restored the native tigers to power in Port Carnelian
Name: 霸权: 玛瑙港事务

Description: 上帝保佑不朽的女王陛下.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Recovering~5|Renascent~7|Glorious~2|Promising~3|Significant~4|Substantial~6|Tremendous
Name: 霸权: 伦敦

Description: 看 你那可怕的帝國 混亂已經歸來 光明跪倒 被你毀滅的言辭屠戮 譯註:原文出自 Alexander Pope's Dunciad
Name: 霸权: 无政府主义者

Description: 陽. 太陽. 太陽. 太陽. 太...
LevelDescriptionText: 5|Blazing~7|TRIUMPHANT~4|Burning~3|Radiant~1|Rising~6|Resplendent~2|Gleaming
Name: 霸权: 黎明机器

Description: 汗国的势力正在增长.
Name: 霸权: 汗国

Description: 耐心; 狂暴; 耐心.
Name: 霸權: 孤独的海胆

Description: The nuns endure.
Name: 调查: 修道院岩礁

Description: 你已经见到了古大陆的心流出的血液之河.
Name: 调查: 亚当之路

Description: 你已经见到了海泽中那被光明洗礼过的地方.
Name: 调查: 阿斯蒂沃

Description: You've visited the Fortas Kettle.
Name: 调查: 爱古

AvailableAt: 在安忒获取港口报告并交给海军.
Description: 你变成安忒的港口报告了吗?
Name: 调查: Anthe

Description: You have seen where the world ends. Behind those peaks of ice, something colder by far.
Name: 调查: 渴求之地平线

Description: 你已经见到了那些人是如何服侍古井的.
Name: 调查: 光之礼拜堂

Description: 山洞里住满了流亡者.
Name: 调查: 法典岛

AvailableAt: 将达哈的港口报告提供给海军.
Description: 你已经探索了达哈.
Name: 调查: 达哈

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Your visit to Demeaux Island has been confirmed by the Admiralty Records Office
Description: 你已经见到了那个蘑菇看上去比表面多得多的地方.
Name: 调查: 德莫岛

Description: 你从偷灵魂的猴子的领地回来了.
Name: 调查: 手掌帝国

Description: 你已经见过了海冰之塔下那些蹲着的人.
Name: 调查: 寒霜城

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Your visit to Gaider's Mourn has been confirmed by the Admiralty Records Office
Description: 你已经见过了那里的灯光和悬崖.
Name: 调查: 加德的哀悼

Description: 你已经见过了倒在海中的破碎城堡.
Name: 调查: 神落

Description: 你已经见过了那些被黎明机器选中的人.
Name: 调查: 宏伟晶洞

Description: 你和坦途做了朋友.
Name: 调查: 隐逸之地

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Your visit to Hunter's Keep has been confirmed by the Admiralty Records Office
Description: An odd place. Best to keep an eye on it.
Name: 调查: 猎户塔楼

Description: 你将从伊瑞暮归来.
Name: 调查: 伊瑞暮

Description: 你已经见过了海盗王的领地.
Name: 调查: 猫岛

Description: 你已经去过了可汗之心, 那里的电灯很亮,几大部族都在磨砺他们的利爪.
Name: 调查: 可汗之心

Description: You've seen where the Khanate rebels lair.
Name: Surveyed: Khan's Shadow

Description: You've seen the hungry place at the world's edge.
Name: Surveyed: Kingeater's Castle

AvailableAt: 将巴内特的港口报告交给海军.
Description: 你已经探索了沉没的巴内特.
Name: 调查: 沉没的巴内特

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Your visit to Mt Palmerston has been confirmed by the Admiralty Records Office
Description: A detailed report on a place of interest. The Admiralty would value it.
Name: 调查: 帕默斯顿山

Description: 你已经去过了巨大大嘴.
Name: 调查: 旮旯

Description: 你已经见过了遗失邮差们的岛屿.
Name: 调查: 农西奥

Description: 你得到了啮齿类动物战争的第一手资料.
Name: 调查: 皮格莫特岛

Description: 你已经见到了产出做劳工的粘土人的城市.
Name: 调查: 碎心国

Description: 把小伦敦消息带给伦敦.
Name: 调查: 玛瑙港

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Your visit to Port Cecil has been confirmed by the Admiralty Records Office
Description: 你已经见到了那个视象棋为圣物的地方.
Name: 调查: 塞西尔港

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Your visit to Quaker's Haven has been confirmed by the Admiralty Records Office
Description: 你已经见过了保管火焰的山岗.
Name: 调查: 贵格避风港

Description: 手工制作愉悦的地方, 所有的东西都有价可循.
Name: 调查: 玫瑰之门

Description: 你从去悲伤蜘蛛躲藏地的旅途中活了下来.
Name: 调查: 救世主岩礁

Description: 你去过了一个记忆之城, 并将自己的一部分抛在了身后.
Name: 调查: 骨雕馆

Description: 至少你可以确认,  他们就在他们现在所说的地方.
Name: 调查: 牧羊人岛

Description: On the very edge of London's influence, curious matters are conducted.
Name: 调查: 要塞 III

Description: 你已经见过了巨龟的漂浮残骸.
Name: 调查: 切洛内特

Description: 你已经见到了深寻王王座附近的东西.
Name: 调查: 深寻王的城堡

Description: 你已经去过了海中巨兽走向死亡的地方.
Name: 调查: 刚特极点

Description: 所有的都很丰裕,所有的都很充实.
Name: 调查: 红树学院

Description: 你已经见到了一个人挖掘秘密太深会发生什么.
Name: 调查: 盐狮

Description: 你见到了真菌之母.
Name: 调查: 世纪之蕈

Description: 你已经找到了蛾子和哀痛的隐秘巢穴.
Name: 调查: 爪下

Description: 这座围墙中的光明之城中酝酿着黑暗的阴谋.
Name: 调查: 瓦尔查斯

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Your visit to Venderbight has been confirmed by the Admiralty Records Office
Description: 你已经见到了这些半死的人会去的地方.
Name: 调查: 文登湾

Description: 你已经见到了只允许一张面孔存在的岛屿.
Name: 调查: 维瑟吉

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Your visit to Whither has been confirmed by the Admiralty Records Office
Description: 你已经见过了那里的冰和盐.
Name: 调查: 何方

Description: 秘密和囚犯都被囚禁在其中.
Name: 调查: 智慧监狱

Description: 你已经见到了破碎船壳的家.
Name: 调查: 船墟

Description: 回忆它,然后点燃一支蜡烛. 再照亮另一个.
Name: 恐怖故事!!

Description: 对辽阔而黑暗的海泽的恐惧, 还有那些更深的东西. [用上岸的方式降低恐惧, 尤其是在伦敦. 如果当你回到伦敦时恐惧高于50, 你的恐惧值会下降到50.]
LevelDescriptionText: 100|Crazed~25|Nervous~50|Fearful~75|Haunted~1|Wary~0|Serene
Name: 恐惧

Description: 这几乎不能称得上是一本书. 几打纸片塞进另外两张纸片. 每张上面都印着一条对针对谋杀的有用建议, 还有, 一些血迹.
Name: The Boke of Sharpes

Description: It thrums. It wanders. It has a delightful stink. [This ship is available players who backed Sunless Sea at the Navigator Tier or higher. 它将在日后DLC中开放.]
Name: 覆叶之心

ChangeDescriptionText: 0|Avernus: grey rock and blue water.~1|Naples: crowded streets and the sea's horizon~10|Vienna: revolution in the air
Description: 你离家很远.
LevelDescriptionText: 0|Avernus~1|Naples~10|Vienna
Name: 阳光的残酷行为

ChangeDescriptionText: 5|Who will the corpse go to?~1|Bound for Hunter's Keep.~10|Bound for Station III.~30|Bound for Nuncio with the Drownie Postman.~15|You witnessed history.~35|Scheduled for redelivery.
Description: 这是能冲上岸的最可怕也最罕见的东西.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Bound for Hunter's Keep~5|Who will the corpse go to?~10|Bound for Station III with the Anxious University Student~30|Bound for Nuncio with the Drownie Postman~15|You witnessed the Anxious University Student relive history through the needle.~35|You allowed the Drownies to fulfil their concord with the Lorn-Flukes.
Name: 棘刺的命运

Description: 她的诗或许结束了.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|The past has been denied~10|Verse has proven persuasive~20|Authority has been restored~25|A duel has been won~30|The Modiste is triumphant~0|The Poet has been captured
Name: 海盗诗人的命运

Description: 她的丈夫去了花之城吗?
Name: 暴躁的慈善家: 安忒

Description: 他寻找过和平之城吗?
Name: 暴躁的慈善家: 达哈

Description: 也许他藏在了海兽走向死亡的地方.
Name: 暴躁的慈善家: 刚特极点

Description: 她的丈夫逃去了难民之城吗?
Name: 暴躁的慈善家: 隐逸之地

Description: 她的丈夫逃去自由之城了吗?
Name: 暴躁的慈善家: 旮旯
暴躁的慈善家: 追踪中

Description: 她的丈夫在回忆之城吗?
Name: 暴躁的慈善家: 骨雕馆

Description: 这个奇怪的骷髅曾经是切洛内特巨大蠕虫牵引的祭司战舰的船首装饰.
Name: 食名者的船首像

Description: "这些就是驱动着巴扎的力量." 涡轮机运转着,发出巨量的热量.
Name: 辉煌涡轮机

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You are defiant.
Description: 你根本不关心这些神,无论是真实的还是虚构的. 你会走你自己的路. [这不会让你免遭海泽中神的诅咒.]
LevelDescriptionText: 0|You are not yet defiant
Name: 海泽的神: 蔑视

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You now have the Gods of the Zee: Salt's Attention.
Description: 它在看着你; 如果它真的存在.
Name: 海泽之神: 盐神的注意

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Salt's curse lies on you
Description: 诅咒降临到你身上: 无名的告别之神的诅咒.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Salt's curse lies on you
Name: 海泽之神: 盐神的诅咒

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You know something of the three gods of the zee.
Description: 海泽中存在着一些强大的力量.
Name: 海泽之神: 石头, 风暴和盐

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You now have the Gods of the Zee: Stone's Attention.
Description: 它在很远的地方;但是也许它在注意着你.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|You now have the Gods of the Zee: Stone's Attention
Name: 海泽之神: 石神的注意

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Stone's Curse lies on you.
Description: 你带上了一个诅咒: 家与治愈的无名神的诅咒.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Stone's Curse lies on you
Name: 海泽之神: 石的诅咒

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You now have the Gods of the Zee: Storm's Attention.
Description: 古代的愤怒现在知道了你的存在.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|You now have the Gods of the Zee: Storm's Attention
Name: 海泽之神: 风暴神的注意

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Storm's curse lies on you
Description: 诅咒降临到你身上: 高处与愤怒的无名神的诅咒.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Storm's curse lies on you
Name: 海泽之神: 风暴神的诅咒

Description: 来自它甲壳质核心的最古老最致命的蜘蛛状生物. 最致命的,感谢上天它死了.
Name: 世纪之树的心

Description: "这里记录了一些穿越[xxxxx] 的细节,在[xxxxxx]的陪伴执行, 在 [xxxxxx]上...." [用这个提高你的交流值.未来的船长可以一直使用它除非你将它卖掉.]
Name: 地平线法典

Description: 你们究竟是在哪里遇到的, 又一次?是纹身师克拉瑟莫特介绍你们认识的吗?
Name: 紫丁香色的女士

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|The Last Constable has been seen on Demeaux Island.
Description: 她在孢子中找到了一个藏身地吗?
LevelDescriptionText: 1|You have not looked for her on Demeaux Island
Name: 最后的治安官: 德莫岛

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|The Last Constable has been seen in Gaider's Mourn
Description: 她将正义带给了海盗之林的海盗们吗?
LevelDescriptionText: 1|You have not looked for her in Gaider's Mourn
Name: 最后的治安官: 加德的哀悼

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|The Last Constable has been seen in Khan's Heart.
Description: 她会藏在伦敦的敌国吗?
LevelDescriptionText: 1|You have not looked for her in Khan's Heart
Name: 最后的治安官: 可汗之心

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You are looking for the Last Constable.
Description: 你在这里找她, 你在那里找她.
Name: 最后的治安官: 寻找中

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|The Last Constable has been seen in Venderbight.
Description: 她在这些半死不活的人之中工作吗?
LevelDescriptionText: 1|You have not looked for her in Venderbight
Name: 最后的治安官: 文登湾

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You have the Mark of the East.
Description: 苍老的灵魂啊. 你要去哪里, 苍老的灵魂?
LevelDescriptionText: 1|You have the Mark of the East
Name: 东方的印记

Description: 这就是他存放在寒霜城的设计图.
Name: 机械师的秘密

Description: 她对见血表示无所谓. 但是她非常不喜欢衣服上的血污.
Name: 无情的衣帽商

Description: 它不是个有吸引力的东西. 也许你不会把它留在壁炉架上.
Name: 无情衣帽商的心

Description:
一本为孩子写的书. 每一页上都是一种地表无法找到但是却存在于地下的颜色.

[你每找到一种不可能的颜色都可以返回到监护官这里. 书页给了你一些线索, 但是你需要在远方的港口找到它们.]
Name: 地虹

Description: 传奇  谜团. 在碎心国有个位置等着她.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Art has been denied~10|The power of verse~20|Authority is restored~25|A duel has been won~30|The Modiste is triumphant
Name: 海盗诗人

Description: 他将他的复仇暂时搁置.
Name: 谨慎的魔术师

LevelDescriptionText: 2|You carry a wax-paper missive from the Conodont in Nook, to a friend in Anthe~3|You carry a reply from the Conodont's sister.
Name: 老鳗的尊重

Description: 他有着把敌人的墓土压实后的那种满意笑容.
Name: 满足的魔术师

Description: 她是猎户塔楼的三姐妹中最年轻的. 现在她已无家可归. 她不会向你展示她的脸, 更不会说发生了什么,但是她已经准备好用她的知识治愈你的船员...
Name: 伤痕累累的妹妹

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You have the Scars of the North.
Description: 无法容留你的地方, 压碎了你. 你身上依旧有伤势.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|You have the Scars of the North
Name: 北方的伤痕

Description: 用一根丝带封起. 总之那看起来像是一根丝带.
Name: 学者的笔记

Description: 一个用玻璃和钢铁制造的复杂机器,闪着光. 在它的核心,一只蛇王怒吼着. 也许是魔术师在哀求着.
Name: 蛇纹机

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You have brought the Snow Child aboard.~0|The Snow Child has departed.
Description: 每天它都会融化一点.
Name: 雪孩子

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You have the Touch of the South.
Description: 古大陆的光在你的血液中涌动.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|You have the Touch of the South
Name: 南方的碰触

Description: 有些银色的东西在他的眼中闪烁着.
Name: 彬彬有礼的魔术师

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You have the Western Stigma.
Description: 你见到了黎明机器之后的东西
LevelDescriptionText: 1|You have the Western Stigma
Name: 西方的烙印

Description: 他们会因此记住你.
Name: 海泽之歌

Description: 时间正在流逝!
Name: 剩下的时间...

AvailableAt: 有时候可以在伦敦雇用他, 但他更经常出现在遥远北方的某个港口.
Description: 他从没睡过? 他的眼睛下有重重的黑眼圈, 但是他的手依旧很稳.
Name: 不知疲倦的机械师

Description: 技术上来讲他们是乘客而不是货物. 但是你永远不知道他们是否会说些什么. [死亡聚居地会为这些乘客买单: 把他们在那里卖掉.]
Name: 死亡侨民

Description: 一定是猴子遗孤丢掉的.
Name: 雪孩子的牙齿

Description: 我们这个时代最惊人的巧合, 鱼雷是 '鱼形'的. [鱼雷射击需要的弹药.]
Name: 鱼雷

Description: 在战斗中部署鱼雷网能够很好的防御鱼雷的攻击!
Name: 鱼雷网

Description: Deployed protection against torpedoes, expressed as %
Name: Torpedo Protection

Description: 这决定了鱼雷攻击的效率.这只在一些增强型设备上有.
Name: Torpedo Tubes

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You now have a Trophy: A Collection of Teeth.
Description: 每颗牙都是从不同的嘴里拔下来的. [你之前的那个船长是一名低贱的食人者,服务于光之礼拜堂和那个溺死的人]
Name: 纪念品: 一些牙齿

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You now have a Trophy: A Family Portrait.
Description: 很正式的纪念照. 被雨水浸湿的名字很难读出来. [在你之前的那名船长找到并埋葬了他父亲的遗骨,或者遗骨的代替品.]
Name: 纪念品: 作为纪念的银版相片

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You now have a Trophy: a Family Bible.
Description: 当然是雅各书. 其中一段被红墨水圈了起来, 墨迹已经很久了 - 罗马书 6:9. [你的前任船长之一实现了不朽, 或者推翻了不朽.]
Name: 纪念品: 家庭圣经

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You now have a Trophy: A Family Portrait.
Description: 照片上的人有一个共同点. 他们都在微笑. [你之前的那名船长找到并救出了他的父亲.]
Name: 纪念品: 一张全家福

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You now have a Trophy: A Folded Flag.
Description: 一面从海泽远方的迷你国家来的不平凡的旗帜.
Name: 纪念品: 折叠的旗帜

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You now have a Trophy: A Letter of Commendation.
Description: 神秘的邮政局长亲自签署的这封信. [你之前的船长在寄错的邮包中找到了骨头.]
Name: 纪念品: 一封嘉奖信

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You now have a Trophy: A Model Monster.
Description: 一个海怪镇纸, 用阴暗黑骨雕得很漂亮. [你之前的船长被证明是海怪之子]
Name: 纪念品: 典型的怪物

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You now have a Trophy: A Posthumous Medal.
Description: 社会人士和海员为他进行了募捐. [你之前的船长的父亲牺牲了自己来拯救他的船员.]
Name: 纪念品: 死后的奖章

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You now have a Trophy: A Shattered Coral Knife.
Description: 这些碎片被骄傲地展示在饰板上. [你之前的船长在噬王者的城堡里找到了遗骨]
Name: 纪念品: 一把破碎的珊瑚刀

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You now have a Trophy: An Autographed Copy of the Zong of the Zee.
Description: 这也是第一版. [你之前的船长完成了一部关于海泽的史诗.]
Name: 纪念品: 海泽之歌的手稿

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You now have a Trophy: An Impossible Restaurant Bill.
Description: 书桌的抽屉里摞着这些餐厅的账单,加起来是一艘普通船只的价格的三倍. [你之前的船长赢得了财富并在舒适中退休.]
Name: 纪念品: 不可思议的餐厅账单

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You now have a Trophy: Not Quite Human.
Description: 这曾经是某人吗? [你之前的船长发现他作为海怪的那一部分, 并且抛弃了他作为人类的存在.
Name: 纪念品: 不完全是人类

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You now have a Trophy: Restless.
Description: 你的书房里挂着一幅画, 是一个熟铁打造的浮标, 永无尽头地漂浮着, 光线刺穿了海泽的黑暗.你几乎能听到那钟声. [你之前的船长越过了世界的最东方.]
Name: 纪念品: 没有尽头

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You now have a Trophy: the Lights of London.
Description: 你的书房里挂着一幅画. 两名旅者在眺望着, 永远保持着这个姿势,就像他们目的地的光已经很近了. [你之前的船长越过了世界的最东方.]
Name: 纪念品: 伦敦的灯火

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You now have a Trophy: Those Final Mountains.
Description: 你的书房里挂着一幅画, 看起来像是一座不可能存在的山上缠绕着的迷雾. [你之前的船长越过了世界的最东方.]
Name: 纪念品: 最终之山

Description: 他们在屋顶上制造了这些, 并且不会说为什么. [一件一次性物品,在战斗中对双方产生无法照亮的黑暗, 增加恐惧.]
Name: Unclear Device

Description: 什么在黄铜大使馆等待着女恶魔?
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Hell will welcome the Deviless~2|Hell believes the Deviless is a traitor
Name: 未被揭露的秘密: 地狱的命运

Description: 深处到处都是通道.那些饥饿的人留下了什么?
Name: 未被揭露的秘密: 破碎的城堡

Description: 你已拥有 潜艇DLC.
Name: 海泽之下

ChangeDescriptionText: 3|The letter has clearly been opened.~2|No one could tell it's been read. Could they?~1|You've accepted a farewell letter to be delivered to Hideaway.
Description: 来自一位几乎已死的人的信, 向隐逸之地的一位爱人告别.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Unopened and pristine~2|Stealthily read~3|Clearly perused
Name: 爪下: 向隐逸之地送一封告别信

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You have an important letter to deliver.~2|No one will ever know. Right?~3|The letter was open when you got it.
Description: 你要送一封重要的信. [在物品栏中查看信件来确认目的地位置.]
LevelDescriptionText: 1|You have an important letter to deliver.~2|You've stealthily read the letter.~3|The letter has clearly been opened.
Name: 爪下: 送信

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You've accepted a letter of apology to be delivered to Nook.~2|No one could tell it's been read. Could they?~3|The letter has clearly been opened.
Description: 来自一位几乎已死的人的信, 给旮旯的同志的道歉.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Unopened and pristine~2|Stealthily read~3|Clearly perused
Name: 爪下: 向旮旯送一封道歉信

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You've accepted a love letter to be delivered to Anthe.~2|No one could tell it's been read. Could they?~3|The letter has clearly been opened.
Description: 来自一位几乎已死的人的信, 向安忒的某人宣读其永恒的爱.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Unopened and pristine~2|Stealthily read~3|Clearly perused
Name: 爪下: 向安忒送一封关于爱的信

Description: 这个几乎已死的人如何面对他的死亡?
Name: 爪下: 将死的优雅

Description: 一位不动感情的人, 喜欢摆弄标本针和那些玻璃罐, 他正在寻找罕见的鳞翅目昆虫.
Name: 爪下: 举世无双的昆虫学者

Description: 与其说是尸体, 不如说是一件刚脱下的西装. 尽管如此, 他在德莫港的兄弟也许想知道.
Name: 爪下: 洛伦佐的外套

ChangeDescriptionText: 2|There are trespasses to be forgiven.~102|Lorenzo has shed his life, but his light lingers in his friends.~1|You have met an Almost Dead Man in the Undercrow.~3|Saying farewell to a lover in Hideaway.	~5|Delivering a lover's wordless response.	~10|A mercenary in Nook deserves an apology.~15|Delivering a wronged comrade's retribution.~20|A pledge of undying love to one in Anthe.~25|Delivering news of a lover's warm response.~30|Nothing more to be said.~26|Delivering news of a lover's fiery reaction.	~50|The end nears.~100|Lorenzo has shed his life.~110|Lorenzo has shed this life, and his light has been extinguished.
Description: 几乎死去的人希望问心无愧地结束这复杂的生命.
LevelDescriptionText: 2|There are trespasses to be forgiven.~3|Saying farewell to a lover in Hideaway.~100|Lorenzo has shed this life.~102|Lorenzo has shed this life, but his light lingers in his friends.~1|You have met an Almost Dead Man in the Undercrow.~5|Delivering a lover's wordless response.~10|A mercenary in Nook deserves an apology.~15|Delivering a wronged comrade's retribution.~20|A pledge of undying love to one in Anthe.~25|Delivering news of a lover's warm response.~30|Nothing more to be said.~9|There are trespasses to be forgiven.~19|There are trespasses to be forgiven.~7|Rid of a farewell letter.~17|Rid of an apology letter.~27|Rid of a love letter.~26|Delivering news of a lover's fiery reaction.	.~50|The end nears.~110|Lorenzo has shed this life. Now his companion is due for Adam's Way.
Name: 爪下: 几乎已死的人

Description: 最好不要读, 嗯?
Name: 未经阅读的日志

Description: 他一直在看着.他不会眨眼.
Name: 令人不安的贤者

Description: 一箱特别的人类灵魂. 它永远也不会知道皇家海关的印章长什么样子. 因此, 它不能在市场中出售,你最好别在带着这些的时候被人抓到.
Name: 一箱未盖章的卓越灵魂

Description: 一箱正在哀求的灵魂. 它上面没有盖海关的印章 - 这是走私货!
Name: 一箱未盖章的灵魂

Description: 一个果实,一个珠宝,还是一滴眼泪? 让植物学家来鉴定它吧.它尝起来有点像松果.
Name: 世纪之蕈的孢子

Description: 你知道了去医院的路, 还有去警卫室和米希尔庙的.
Name: 瓦尔查斯: 瓦尔查斯的守卫为你指路

Description: 这可能是件好事?
Name: 瓦尔查斯: 大司焰的兴趣

Description: 这很难得.
Name: 瓦尔查斯: 表情严肃的护士的认可

Description: 这看起来并没有坏处; 最坏会发生什么?
Name: 瓦尔查斯: 戴镶宝石头巾年轻人的邀请

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|The first Tower-bell has sounded.~2|The second Tower-bell has sounded.~3|The third Tower-bell has sounded.~4|The fourth Tower-bell has sounded.~5|The fifth Tower-bell has sounded: it is evening.~6|It is night, although there is no darkness in Varchas. Time to sleep.~7|Your permitted time in Varchas is over. Time to go; until next time.
Description: 瓦尔查斯有五座镜塔. 当每座塔都敲响过大钟后,夜幕就降临了.
Name: 瓦尔查斯: 塔楼上的钟声

Description: 他们崇拜瓦尔查斯的太阳, 并且已经把黑暗从城市中流放出去.
Name: 瓦尔查斯: 镜之城

Description: 通过汗水与伤痕得到的尊重
Name: 瓦尔查斯: 守卫的尊重

Description: 西部主镜的管理者兄弟; 对黑眼的男孩和酒没有抵抗力.
Name: 瓦尔查斯: 迟缓的点灯者

Description: 速度,隐藏,欺诈. 降低敌人能够发现你的距离.
Name: 面纱值

Description: 黑色的,雕刻着一些卷曲的记号.
Name: 冒险家的奖章

Description: 红色的. 像血该有的颜色. 但是更红, 更深, 还活着.
Name: 一瓶高度可疑的血

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You are smuggling a proscribed cargo of red honey.
Description: 每一个仔细填满垫料的箱子里都装了十瓶. [这东西就算是合法使用也太过危险. 把它带到伦敦时要格外小心.]
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Smuggling a proscribed cargo of red honey
Name: 一小瓶红蜂蜜

Description: 把它放到你的罗盘上,  用海蝙蝠的血喂它. 它会指引你的.
Name: 警醒的雕像

Description: 一些关于如何扮演这些角色的知识. [有时候, 无知即是自由. 学到更多会造成更复杂的效应.]
LevelDescriptionText: 3|Aware of Visitor Roles~4|Aware of Moth Role~7|Aware of Higher Roles
Name: 维瑟吉: 一部分所需的知识

Description: 带着光进入到黑暗的地带.
LevelDescriptionText: 2|Empty-handed~3|Carrying a flare and nervous~4|Empty-handed and nervous~5|Carrying a flare and brave~6|Empty-handed and brave~10|Violator of the Sacred Mysteries~1|Carrying a flare~9|Respecter of the Sacred Mysteries~11|Respectful Scholar of the Mysteries~12|Impertinent Scholar of the Mysteries
Name: 维瑟吉: 参加仪式

Description: 维瑟吉为你分配的角色.
LevelDescriptionText: 0|Unmasked~1|Bat Mask~2|Frog Mask~3|Locust Mask~4|Moth Mask~5|Mask of the Risen Sun
Name: 维瑟吉:你的面具

Description: 在远远的高处, 阳光依旧闪耀. [在文登湾, 他们一直渴望了解地面的景象与消息.]
Name: 地面的风景

Description: 非常关键,非常有价值. 没了它们我们该做什么?尤其是当我们是间谍,外交官或者海盗的时候.
Name: 关键情报

Description: 它的眼中闪着警惕的光. 它的忧郁已经消散: 现在你似乎有了某种预感.
Name: 警觉的雕像

Description: 一个看起来很阴险的小雕像... 但是它的眼神却带着某种恳求.
Name: 警惕的古董

Description: 我們會工作.我們只會工作. [这三个粘土司炉会降低你需要的船员数量,但是也会降低船员容量, 轻微提升引擎功率.它们放在附属物槽位.当他们被卸下来时, 他们会耐心地站着,手牵着手,带着不可读的灰色眼神. 其中一个有时会说: "我喜歡它安靜的樣子."]
Name: 我們是粘土

Description: 血液缓慢地从它的四周溢出, 被吸入那个伤疤.
Name: 哭泣的伤疤

Description: "哦,是的, 今晚那个淹死的人在哼唱, 一首水中的歌就像鱼骨一样."
Name: 低语的战利品箱

Description: 说出正确的密语, 齿轮就会排成一列为盒子解锁. 但是正确的密语是什么? [令人惊恐的学者也许会知道些什么.]
Name: 被密语锁住的谜题之盒

AvailableAt: 用一枚闪晶在深寻王处交换; 可以抵消达哈的幻境.
Description: 据说如果你需要打破达哈的幻境, 那么你需要吃掉它. 但是请小心.
Name: 白色鲈花

Description: 像盐一样锋利,像冰一样透明的玻璃.
Name: 何方聚光镜

Description: 她知道火焰的用法. 但是她并不适应海泽. 把她带到伦敦, 去黄铜大使馆.
Name: Wistful Deviless

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You witnessed the Curator's Emergence
Description: "...死亡侨民不会完全死去.许多人的结局都在大疗养院里, 在没有感觉的恐惧中慢慢枯萎. (这还没被公开过.)少数人的结局非常迅速: 转变成一种携带翅膀和知识的生物, 还有一种结局也许是升华, 成为一枚卵或者之类的东西. 这个值一千元以及邪恶和罪恶的诱惑..."
LevelDescriptionText: 1|You witnessed the Curator's Emergence
Name: 目击: 监护官的结局

Description: 你被告知了一项深深伤害到你的真相.
Name: 令人伤感的真相

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You're going to Port Carnelian.~2|You're going to Polythreme.~3|You're going to Port Cavendish.
Description: 你不能允许船墟人危害无辜. 尤其是那些会为你的警告付钱的无辜.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Port Carnelian~2|Polythreme~3|Port Cavendish
Name: 船墟: 一个保存船只的城市

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|The Fair King has requested you bury your offering of scintillack in Dahut.~5|You buried the scintillack in Dahut. Who knows what it may grow into?	~10|You kept the scintillack for yourself. Who'll ever be the wiser?
Description: 当被系缆拴住的两人第一次交换礼物时, 习俗是将礼物埋在达哈.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|The Fair King has requested you bury your offering of scintillack in Dahut~5|You buried the scintillack in Dahut. Who knows what it may grow into?~10|You kept the scintillack for yourself. Who'll ever be the wiser?
Name: 船墟: 废墟仪式

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Find a jarful of tether in Wrack.~5|Bring the jarful of tether to the Severe Chemist, who waits on the Uttershroom.~10|A satisfied client.~25|A joy forever.
Description: 想要研究系缆藻的药剂师.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Bring the Chemist a jarful of tether from Wrack~5|The Severe Chemist is waiting on the Uttershroom to collect his jarful of tether~10|You delivered the jarful of tether to the Severe Chemist~25|You tasted the tether, instead of delivering it to the Severe Chemist
Name: 船墟: 帮助研究

ChangeDescriptionText: 5|The Fair King will not easily part from his mirror.~10|You may speak to Bourdain on your ship.~15|You have recruited Bourdain.
Description: 平明王最珍视的财产. 顺带, 其中包含七人团之一布尔丹最后的那部分.
LevelDescriptionText: 5|The Fair King will not easily part from his mirror~10|You may speak to Bourdain on your ship~15|You recruited Bourdain
Name: 船墟: 对镜子的欲望

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|You're going to Gaider's Mourn.~2|You're going to Khan's Heart.~3|You're going to the Tomb-Colony of Venderbight.
Description: 去往港口劝说船长开往船墟上方水域.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Gaider's Mourn~2|Khan's Heart~3|Venderbight
Name: 船墟: 船墟人的新猎获

ChangeDescriptionText: 2|Are you quite yourself?~1|Do not fear. All shall be well.~3|Your eyes are wider.
Description: 回忆前来.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Do not fear. All shall be well~2|Are you quite yourself?~3|Your eyes are wider
Name: 船墟: 回忆

ChangeDescriptionText: 5|There will be something beautiful.
Description: 有些东西会在达哈生长.
Name: 船墟: 蓝宝石盛开

Description: 从每一艘被毁的船上收来. 将其交给船墟. 你就可以尝到系缆藻. 尝到爱的味道.
Name: 船墟: 废品

Description: 你的言语将会把它们沉入海中.
Name: 船墟: 送去船墟的船

Description: 你已经了解了爱. 爱不会消散.
Name: 船墟: 系缆藻的味道

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|The city is in want.~17|The city is thriving!
Description: 船墟的居民依赖于沉船. 他们是怎么发展的?
LevelDescriptionText: 17|A City of Pleasures	~10|A City that Struggles~13|A City that Survives~1|A City of Want
Name: 船墟: 城市的状况

ChangeDescriptionText: 3|You shared a vision of romance with the Fair King.~1|There was a romance.~2|Have you seen something of the Vibrant Lady in the Fair King?
Description: 往事, 如旧.
LevelDescriptionText: 3|You shared a vision of romance with the Fair King	~1|You had a vision of a romance~2|Have you seen something of the Vibrant Lady in the Fair King?
Name: 船墟: 关于骨的幻觉

ChangeDescriptionText: 3|You shared a vision of friendship with the Fair King.~1|There is a friendship.~2|Have you seen something of the Jocular Gentleman in the Fair King?
Description: 是什么? 是什么.
LevelDescriptionText: 3|You shared a vision of friendship with the Fair King	~1|You had a vision of a friendship~2|Have you seen something of the Jocular Gentleman in the Fair King?
Name: 船墟: 关于酒杯的幻觉

ChangeDescriptionText: 3|You shared a vision of respect with the Fair King.~1|A partnership will be founded.~2|Have you seen something of the Sharp Driver in the Fair King?
Description: 将会是什么? 会是什么
LevelDescriptionText: 3|You shared a vision of respect with the Fair King	~1|You had a vision of a partnership~2|Have you seen something of the Sharp Driver in the Fair King?
Name: 船墟: 匕首的幻觉

ChangeDescriptionText: 100|You shall be timeless lovers.~200|You shall be famous friends.~300|You shall be co-conquerors of the world.~400|You shall discover what you are - in this time, in this life - together.~500|You are nothing.~3|What are you two to be?~1|You are acquainted with the Fair King.~101|You have discovered another aspect of your love.~201|You have discovered another aspect of your friendship.~301|You have discovered another aspect of your partnership.~401|You have discovered another aspect of yourselves.~501|You are still nothing.~2|What do have you shared?
Description: 你对他来说是什么?
LevelDescriptionText: 100|Timeless lovers~200|Famous friends~300|Co-conquerors of the world~400|Discovering what you are - in this time, in this life - together~500|You are nothing~3|What are you two to be?~1|You are acquainted with the Fair King~2|You shared something with the Fair King
Name: 船墟: 和平明王的关系

AvailableAt: 有时候它也会潜伏在伦敦的港口里.
Description: 它的坏脾气让它失去了船员的宠幸,但是这也让它成为了一只很有效率的捕鼠者 .
Name: 不幸的莫格

Description: 你可以在富含氧气的旮旯水中呼吸 - 暂时的.
Name: 旮旯: 耐受旮旯之水
你对某些东西的恐惧甚于死亡

Description: 背了一身债的忧郁老流浪汉. 带他回家. [当你带他回伦敦时,请确认你身上有6000回声的现金.]
Name: 你的父亲

Description: 这些遗骨看起来和普通的骷髅没什么两样,但是你知道这些骨头究竟是谁的.
Name: 父亲的遗骨

ChangeDescriptionText: 4|Speak with the Dark-Spectacled Admiral at the Admiralty~5|Bring two sacks of Darkdrop Coffee from the South for the Bishop of St Fiacre, in London~6|Bring Scintillack, from Port Cecil or elsewhere, to the Gracious Widow in London~53|Seek a parcel with your name in Nuncio, somewhere in the south of the zee~54|Seek Kingeater's Castle, in the far south-east~55|Seek Horizon's Aspect, in the North~56|Seek Visage, somewhere in the south of the zee~100|Visit the Fathomking~200|Fulfil the Fathomking's Requests~300|You have fulfilled the Fathomking's Requests~400|You have a Message for the Chapel of Lights~500|Bring your father back to London~3|Bring a Zee-Ztory, a Memory of Distant Shores and a Tale of Terror to Huffam, in London. [Explore to find these things.]~52|Seek the Bone Men in the Chelonate, in the east of the zee~2|Bring Mutersalt from the North to Slivvy, in London. [You can buy Mutersalt at Whither if you have a Zee-ztories.]
Description: 在你寻找父亲遗骨的路上,下一个难关是什么?
LevelDescriptionText: 100|Visit the Fathomking~4|Speak with the Dark-Spectacled Admiral at the Admiralty~200|Fulfil the Fathomking's Requests~54|Seek Kingeater's Castle, in the far south-east~53|Seek a parcel with your name in Nuncio, somewhere in the south of the zee~56|Seek Visage, somewhere in the south of the zee~52|Seek the Bone Men in the Chelonate, in the east of the zee~300|Fathomking's Requests Fulfilled~55|Seek Horizon's Aspect, in the North~400|A Message for the Chapel of Lights~3|Bring a Zee-Ztory, a Memory of Distant Shores and a Tale of Terror to Huffam, in London~5|Bring two sacks of Darkdrop Coffee from the South for the  Bishop of St Fiacre, in London~2|Bring Mutersalt from the North to Slivvy, in London~6|Bring Scintillack, from Port Cecil or elsewhere, to the Gracious Widow in London
Name: Your Father's Bones: A Cold Trail

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|The Fathomking has requested a Legend's Heart~0|You have fulfilled the Fathomking's request for a Legend's Heart
Description: 这是最强大的海怪:流浪之山或者世纪之树的心, 也许.
Name: 父亲的遗骨: 为深寻王准备的传奇之心

ChangeDescriptionText: 0|You have fulfilled the Fathomking's request for a Miracle of Science~1|The Fathomking has requested a Miracle of Science
Description: 带来一件卓越的引擎或者武器.你的船官会帮上忙的.
Name: 父亲的遗骨: 为深寻王准备的科学奇迹

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|The Fathomking has requested a Sky-Light~0|You have fulfilled the Fathomking's request for a Sky-Light
Description: 为深寻王带来阳光... 或者那些可以冒充阳光的东西.
Name: 父亲的遗骨: 为深寻王准备的天空之光

ChangeDescriptionText: 0|You have fulfilled the Fathomking's request for a Willing Guest~1|The Fathomking has requested a Willing Guest
Description: 把一名船官带给深寻王. 选择一名完成了海上事务的船官, 而且想要留在深寻王的堡垒里的人. 也许某个喜欢海鲜的家伙会想要这么做.
Name: 父亲的遗骨: 为深寻王准备的一名自愿的宾客

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|The Fathomking has requested an account of an Eldest's End~0|You have fulfilled the Fathomking's request for an account of an Eldest's End
Description: 深寻王想要你去见证一些最古老的存在的死亡, 并回来.
Name: 父亲的遗骨: 为深寻王准备的一个远古之物的结局

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|The Fathomking has requested the Fruit of an Eternal Tree~0|You have fulfilled the Fathomking's request for the Fruit of an Eternal Tree
Description: 找到那棵不死之树的果实.
Name: 父亲的遗骨: 为深寻王带来的永恒之树的果实

ChangeDescriptionText: 2|You have a stolen bone to return to the Chelonate.~3|You have the delivery address for Nuncio~6|You have a slip of paper with the name of a mask from VIsage~4|You have a knife to match with the one at Kingeater's Castle~5|The Location of a Stone Fragment from Avid Horizon
Description: 深寻王给了你需要的东西. 把它带到你的目的地去.
LevelDescriptionText: 2|A Stolen Bone for the Chelonites~6|The Name of a Mask~7|A Message for the Chapel of Lights~3|A Delivery Address for Nuncio~4|A coral-bladed knife matching one in Kingeater's Castle~5|The Location of a Stone Fragment from Avid Horizon
Name: 父亲的遗骨: 深寻王的钥匙

Description: 关于海浪和海浪下面的奇怪故事.那些海浪之下的要更奇怪些.
Name: Zee-ztory

ChangeDescriptionText: 1|Your ship may now transform into a zubmarine! Press 'T' when at zee to transform.
Description: 按 'T' 来将你的船变形为潜艇或者变回船.
LevelDescriptionText: 1|Your ship is capable of zubmarine travel.
Name: 潜艇

Description: 汤的颜色就像是雪地上的风干血迹. 汤的味道就像是蘑菇,辣椒和铁锈混在一起的味道. 至于配方,被严格保密.
Name: 滋滋汤

AvailableAt: 在面纱花园尝试囚徒之蜜
Description: 囚徒之蜜会打开多少扇门? 这会为你开启Zero Summer (查看上方提示条)的一个额外初始选项 以及其他StoryNexus 的游戏世界...
Name: 对镜中世界的一瞥
